00:46:22.848 --> 00:46:25.884
Hey, you would, too, if you was the one that sold me this rope.
嘿，要是俺告诉你，这条绳子是你卖我的，你也会的。


713
00:46:26.602 --> 00:46:28.061
Good point, John.
问得好，约翰。


714
00:46:29.146 --> 00:46:30.397
He's a good boy.
他是个好孩子。


715
00:46:30.564 --> 00:46:31.648
He ain't done nothing.
他不会干坏事的。


716
00:46:31.857 --> 00:46:32.941
Duke, don't hurt him.
杜克，别弄伤他。


717
00:46:33.108 --> 00:46:35.527
Emmett, come on over here, boy.Hold onto this rope.
艾默特，到这儿来，孩子。抓住绳子。


718
00:46:35.694 --> 00:46:37.154
There's a boy.
这孩子能干的。


719
00:46:37.321 --> 00:46:38.530
You know this boy's family as well as I.
你和我一样，也都认识这孩子的家庭。


720
00:46:38.697 --> 00:46:39.948
That's right.I do. I know.
这就对了。我知道我认识他家。


721
00:46:40.115 --> 00:46:41.049
And you know he's a good boy.
而你也知道，他是个好孩子。


722
00:46:41.116 --> 00:46:42.284
They're good people.They're good people,
他们是好人，他们都是好人，


723
00:46:42.451 --> 00:46:44.219
but we got a dilemma here, John.
但是我们骑虎难下了，约翰。


724
00:46:44.286 --> 00:46:46.997
We got a dilemma. I'm going to tell you what it is.
我们是骑虎难下。我告诉该怎么办。


725
00:46:47.164 --> 00:46:48.665
Hounds don't lie.
猎犬不会说谎。


726
00:46:48.832 --> 00:46:49.750
Be a man, now.
现在，你长大了。


727
00:46:49.917 --> 00:46:52.753
You got to take that rope and snap, crack.
你抓住绳子，使劲一拉，啪的一下。


728
00:46:52.920 --> 00:46:55.798
Can't lynch that boy, Ellis.Can't lynch him.
你不能私刑处置那个孩子，艾利斯。不能用私刑。


729
00:46:55.964 --> 00:46:58.050
I ain't going to let nobody get hanged.
我不会让任何人被绞死的。


730
00:46:58.217 --> 00:47:00.010
I ain't going to let it happen.It won't happen.
我不会让这种事发生的。它不会发生。


731
00:47:00.219 --> 00:47:01.929
Now grab that rope.Come on, grab it.
现在抓住这绳子，来吧，抓住它。


732
00:47:02.096 --> 00:47:05.307
About 4 summers ago,I went over to Chiefland.
大约4年前的夏天，我去了奇夫兰。


733
00:47:05.474 --> 00:47:07.643
A colored boy over there was looking in the window...
那边有个黑人男孩正从窗户往里看…


734
00:47:07.810 --> 00:47:10.312
at a white girl watching her take a bath.
他在偷看一个白人女孩洗澡。


735
00:47:10.479 --> 00:47:11.647
Did he say something?
他说了什么没有？


736
00:47:11.814 --> 00:47:13.482
No, he didn't.
没有，他没说什么。


737
00:47:13.690 --> 00:47:15.067
Maybe he don't know nothing if he didn't say nothing.
如果他什么都不说，也许他什么都不知道。


738
00:47:15.234 --> 00:47:19.488
You should have seen them go crazy on that boy.
你真该看看他们对那男孩的疯狂。


739
00:47:19.655 --> 00:47:21.698
Beat him about half to death.
把他揍到半死。


740
00:47:21.865 --> 00:47:23.283
Boy wouldn't stop screaming.
那男孩不停地尖叫。


741
00:47:23.450 --> 00:47:25.536
We helped him to the railroad track. Number 7 come along...
我们把他放到的铁轨上。7号列车开了过来...


742
00:47:27.538 --> 00:47:29.623
cut his head clean off.
把他的头给压碎了。


743
00:47:31.250 --> 00:47:32.876
Niggers don't run around like a chicken.
黑鬼就不应该像小鸡那样乱跑。


744
00:47:33.043 --> 00:47:34.336
Once that head's off,he's dead.
脑袋一掉，他就死定了。


745
00:47:37.297 --> 00:47:39.049
S-Sam Carter.
萨-萨姆.卡特。


746
00:47:39.216 --> 00:47:40.467
Sam Carter?
萨姆.卡特？


747
00:47:40.634 --> 00:47:42.302
What about Sam Carter?
萨姆.卡特怎么了？


748
00:47:42.469 --> 00:47:43.762
What about Sam?
萨姆怎么了？


749
00:47:43.929 --> 00:47:44.863
Sam the blacksmith?
是那个铁匠萨姆吗？


750
00:47:44.930 --> 00:47:45.889
Sam Carter raped Fanny Taylor?
是萨姆.卡特强奸了范妮.泰勒吗？


751
00:47:46.098 --> 00:47:47.641
No.
不是。


752
00:47:47.808 --> 00:47:49.268
A man. A Mason.
另一个人，一个共济会成员。


753
00:47:49.393 --> 00:47:51.061
What man? Who you talking about?
什么人？你在说谁？


754
00:47:51.270 --> 00:47:53.230
Sam took him in the wagon.
萨姆把他放在马车里。


755
00:47:53.397 --> 00:47:54.815
We was holding the oath.
我们都是宣过誓的。


756
00:47:54.982 --> 00:47:56.191
What are you talking about?
你在说什么？


757
00:47:56.358 --> 00:47:57.776
String him up!
把他捆上！


758
00:48:01.405 --> 00:48:02.948
This boy's under arrest!I'm taking him to jail!
这孩子现在被捕了！我要把他送进监狱！


759
00:48:03.115 --> 00:48:04.091
We're going to string this boy up.
我们要把这孩子捆起来。


760
00:48:04.158 --> 00:48:05.409
Oh, no, you ain't!
哦，你们不能这样！


761
00:48:05.617 --> 00:48:07.411
All right, take the boy,but don't you let him go.
好吧，带走这孩子，但别让他跑了。


762
00:48:07.519 --> 00:48:09.513
Hey, don't you worry about what I am or ain't going to do!
嘿，你不用担心我要做什么或不做什么！


763
00:48:09.580 --> 00:48:10.914
You hear me, Poly?
你听见我说的了吗？波利？


764
00:48:11.081 --> 00:48:12.708
- We're going to get Sam.- You get on out of here!
-我们要去找萨姆。-你们最好离开这儿！


765
00:48:12.875 --> 00:48:15.544
Do you understand? You go do it!
你明白吗？你去做你的去！


766
00:48:15.711 --> 00:48:17.921
Hey, listen to me.You go with them.
嘿，听我说，你看着他们。


767
00:48:18.130 --> 00:48:20.632
Don't let them do nothing until I get there, you hear me?
在我到达之前别让他们做任何事，听到了吗？


768
00:48:20.799 --> 00:48:22.760
You go, too.Ellis, you go.
你也跟着去吧，艾利斯。


769
00:48:22.968 --> 00:48:24.428
I'll take old Aaron in.
我把他送回老阿伦那儿。


770
00:48:24.636 --> 00:48:27.222
Them boys is all riled.
那些孩子都被激怒了。


771
00:48:27.431 --> 00:48:29.099
Aaron, this is all your damn fault!
阿伦，这全都因为你！


772
00:48:29.266 --> 00:48:30.476
You should've said something earlier!
你应该早点儿说实话！


773
00:48:30.642 --> 00:48:33.187
Damn!
该死！


774
00:48:39.693 --> 00:48:44.114
Carter! Carter!
卡特！卡特！


775
00:48:47.993 --> 00:48:49.453
Hey, Booker T.
嘿，布克.T。


776
00:48:51.288 --> 00:48:53.248
Up, boy. Up.
抬起来，孩子。抬起来。


777
00:49:51.473 --> 00:49:53.892
Thank you, Mr. Wright.
谢谢你，赖特先生。


778
00:50:07.189 --> 00:50:09.408
Sam, what you know about this Jesse Hunter, boy?
萨姆，你对杰西·亨特了解多少？小子？


779
00:50:09.533 --> 00:50:10.826
I don't know nothing, Mr. Andrews!
我什么都不知道，安德鲁斯先生！


780
00:50:10.993 --> 00:50:12.995
All niggers don't know nothing!Where's Jesse Hunter?
所有的黑鬼都不知道！杰西.亨特在哪里？


781
00:50:13.203 --> 00:50:14.830
Mr. Purdy. Mr. Purdy.
帕迪先生。帕迪先生。


782
00:50:15.038 --> 00:50:18.000
You a Mason.You got to believe me.
你也是共济会员。你应该相信我。


783
00:50:18.167 --> 00:50:19.877
I don't know no Jesse Hunter!
我真的不知道杰西.亨特！


784
00:50:20.043 --> 00:50:23.505
Yeah, you do,you damn nigger!
是的，你是个该死的黑鬼！


785
00:50:32.222 --> 00:50:33.390
Come on, let him go!
算了吧，让他走吧！


786
00:50:33.557 --> 00:50:35.559
Come on! Hold it! Come on!
行了！住手！差不多了！


787
00:50:35.726 --> 00:50:38.020
He's not against you! Stop it! Stop it!
他不是针对你！你别管！别管！


788
00:50:38.187 --> 00:50:40.230
You shut up and get away!
你闭嘴滚开！


789
00:50:40.439 --> 00:50:41.982
Sam! Get up!
萨姆！起来！


790
00:50:42.149 --> 00:50:44.401
Talk now!
快招了吧！


791
00:50:44.610 --> 00:50:46.570
Talk to me, Sam!
跟我说，萨姆！


792
00:50:46.737 --> 00:50:48.155
Talk to me.
跟我说。


793
00:50:49.490 --> 00:50:50.824
Better say something.
你最好说点什么。


794
00:50:50.991 --> 00:50:52.409
As...
如果...


795
00:50:52.576 --> 00:50:55.704
as God is my witness,
如果上帝替我作证，


796
00:50:55.871 --> 00:50:56.872
I don't know...
我也不知道...


797
00:50:57.039 --> 00:50:58.582
Jesse Hunter.
杰西.亨特。


798
00:50:58.791 --> 00:51:01.168
It was that drifter. That rich nigger from the auction!
是那个流浪汉。拍卖会上那个有钱的黑鬼


799
00:51:01.335 --> 00:51:04.088
That big buck with the black horse,
那个骑着黑马的大个子，


800
00:51:04.254 --> 00:51:06.048
is that him?
是不是他？


801
00:51:10.344 --> 00:51:12.221
Come on, let him talk.
行了，让他说。


802
00:51:12.387 --> 00:51:14.890
Damn you!
你们这帮该死的！


803
00:51:15.057 --> 00:51:17.101
Look at me!
看着我！


804
00:51:17.267 --> 00:51:20.187
Aaron told us you gave him a ride!
阿伦告诉我你带他走了！


805
00:51:20.354 --> 00:51:22.439
Now you show me where you put him out!
现在你告诉我你把他放哪了！


806
00:51:22.648 --> 00:51:25.567
Show me, Sam.I can get you out of here.
告诉我,萨姆。我可以带你离开这里。


807
00:51:25.734 --> 00:51:27.528
Show me, boy.
告诉我，孩子。


808
00:51:27.694 --> 00:51:28.629
You going to show me?
你要告诉我吗？


809
00:51:28.695 --> 00:51:29.613
We going to string you up.
我们要把你捆起来。


810
00:51:29.780 --> 00:51:31.532
Let's go. Get up.
我们走。起来。


811
00:51:31.698 --> 00:51:33.033
Let's go. Get up.
我们走。起来。


812
00:51:35.702 --> 00:51:37.579
If we don't pick up his trail where you say,
如果按你说的我们找不到他的踪迹，


813
00:51:37.746 --> 00:51:39.998
you one dead black son of a bitch.
你这个黑鬼就死定了。


814
00:51:43.168 --> 00:51:45.129
What you got, Earl?
厄尔，你看见什么了？


815
00:51:46.171 --> 00:51:47.297
Nothing, Ellis.
什么都没有，艾利斯。


816
00:51:47.464 --> 00:51:48.841
Nothing?
没有吗？


817
00:51:54.805 --> 00:51:56.723
Y-you can kill me...
你可以杀了我…


818
00:51:58.058 --> 00:51:59.685
but you all...
但你们...


819
00:51:59.852 --> 00:52:01.103
you can't eat me.
不能吃了我。


820
00:52:01.270 --> 00:52:03.730
You ain't no Seminole, boy.
孩子，你再也不是塞米诺人了？


821
00:52:05.315 --> 00:52:07.067
Duke.
杜克。


822
00:52:07.234 --> 00:52:09.069
Get back! Get back!
靠后！靠后！


823
00:52:09.236 --> 00:52:11.321
Damn it, Duke!
该死的，杜克！


824
00:52:11.530 --> 00:52:12.489
What'd you do that for?
你干嘛要这么做？


825
00:52:12.698 --> 00:52:13.657
Goddamn, Duke.
该死的，杜克。


826
00:52:13.824 --> 00:52:16.160
Dumb son of a bitch.
蠢货。


827
00:52:16.326 --> 00:52:18.412
You could've killed me!
你差点杀了我！


828
00:52:18.579 --> 00:52:19.746
He's sure dead.
他肯定死了。


829
00:52:19.913 --> 00:52:21.915
He ain't dead.
他还没死。


830
00:52:22.082 --> 00:52:24.918
Well, let's clean this mess up.
那么，让我们来收拾这烂摊子。


831
00:52:27.588 --> 00:52:28.881
Hang him up in this tree over here.
把他吊在那棵树上。


832
00:52:31.675 --> 00:52:33.552
OK, men, I've had enough of this!
够了，伙计们，我已经受够了！


833
00:52:33.719 --> 00:52:35.445
I'm the law here,you hear me?
我是这里的法律，听见我说的了吗？


834
00:52:35.512 --> 00:52:36.513
Let me in here!
让我在这儿！


835
00:52:36.680 --> 00:52:37.848
Back off now!
现在请回避一下!


836
00:52:38.015 --> 00:52:39.141
Let me in there!
让我在这儿！


837
00:52:41.977 --> 00:52:44.062
Stop it, y'all! Stop it!
住手，你们全都住手！


838
00:52:44.229 --> 00:52:47.065
A white woman was beat and raped...
一名白人妇女被打了还被强奸了...


839
00:52:47.232 --> 00:52:48.567
by a colored boy!
就是这个黑人干的！


840
00:52:48.734 --> 00:52:51.028
Now, you want to tell her husband, her children,
现在，你想告诉她的丈夫，她的孩子们，


841
00:52:51.236 --> 00:52:54.656
that this boy don't have to pay for that?
这个男孩不用为此付出代价吗?


842
00:52:56.241 --> 00:52:57.910
I'm supposed to uphold the law!
我应该维护法律！


843
00:52:58.076 --> 00:52:59.161
Aw, law!
啊，法律！


844
00:52:59.328 --> 00:53:00.829
Whose law, nigger law?
谁的法律？黑鬼的法律？


845
00:53:00.996 --> 00:53:02.873
You wasn't nothing but a damn chicken farmer...
你不过是个养鸡的…


846
00:53:03.040 --> 00:53:05.417
till they gave you that stupid badge!
直到他们发给你这个警徽！


847
00:53:05.584 --> 00:53:07.169
You want to get re-elected?
你还想连任吗？


848
00:53:07.336 --> 00:53:09.254
You want to get re-elected?
你还想连任吗？


849
00:53:09.421 --> 00:53:11.465
- Leave me alone! - Then leave it be!
-别管我！-就让这发生吧！


850
00:53:15.886 --> 00:53:17.721
I got your watch,Sam Carter!
我拿到了你的表，萨姆.卡特！


851
00:53:17.930 --> 00:53:19.348
I got your watch!
我拿到了你的怀表！


852
00:53:37.658 --> 00:53:39.868
You're always so gentle.
你总是那么温柔。


853
00:53:42.579 --> 00:53:44.081
Soft touch.
温柔的抚摸。


854
00:53:45.958 --> 00:53:48.335
You treat me like I'm some kind of angel.
你让我感到我有点像是天使了。


855
00:53:48.502 --> 00:53:51.338
You are an angel to me.
你就是我的天使。


856
00:53:51.505 --> 00:53:53.424
I'm just a woman, James.
我只是一个女人，詹姆斯。


857
00:53:54.883 --> 00:53:56.301
I'm just a woman.
我就是个女人。


858
00:53:58.262 --> 00:54:01.849
Things are getting crazy out there, Fanny.
外面的情况越来越疯狂了，范妮。


859
00:54:02.015 --> 00:54:03.434
They're likely to get worse.
情况可能会变得更糟。


860
00:54:03.600 --> 00:54:05.185
Sam Carter's lynched already.
萨姆.卡特已经被处以私刑。


861
00:54:05.352 --> 00:54:07.396
The blacksmith?
那个铁匠?


862
00:54:07.563 --> 00:54:08.397
What'd he do?
他做什么了？


863
00:54:08.564 --> 00:54:10.691
He give that nigger a ride.
他载了那黑鬼一程。


864
00:54:10.858 --> 00:54:12.818
A ride?
载了一程？


865
00:54:14.111 --> 00:54:15.529
Sam Carter?
萨姆.卡特？


866
00:54:17.281 --> 00:54:18.740
I didn't know.
我不知道。


867
00:54:31.003 --> 00:54:33.630
There's things that I ought to tell you.
有些事情我应该告诉你。


868
00:54:38.469 --> 00:54:40.137
Evening, Mr. Taylor.
晚上好，泰勒先生。


869
00:54:41.180 --> 00:54:45.058
With all that's going on and everything,
发生了这么多事，


870
00:54:45.225 --> 00:54:47.519
we thought y'all could use some hot cooking.
我们觉得你们应该来点热菜。


871
00:54:49.855 --> 00:54:51.940
Thank you kindly, ladies, but my wife ain't feeling too well.
谢谢你们，女士们，但我妻子身体不太舒服。


872
00:54:52.107 --> 00:54:54.067
It's all right, James.
没事的，詹姆斯。


873
00:54:55.402 --> 00:54:57.613
Evening, Miss Walker.
晚上好，沃克小姐。


874
00:54:57.780 --> 00:54:59.364
Oh, Fanny...
噢，范妮...


875
00:54:59.531 --> 00:55:02.493
you poor child.
可怜的孩子。


876
00:55:02.659 --> 00:55:05.996
Oh, I brought you a quilt, too.
我还给你带了被子。


877
00:55:06.163 --> 00:55:07.623
I brought you sweetbread.
我给你带了甜面包。


878
00:55:09.082 --> 00:55:11.668
Don't you worry.That nigger going to be dead...
你别担心。在你吃完这块馅饼之前...


879
00:55:11.877 --> 00:55:14.129
before you finish your pie, OK?
那个黑鬼会被处死的，放心吧？


880
00:55:38.862 --> 00:55:40.322
Get a wagon.
备马车。


881
00:56:21.655 --> 00:56:26.326
Now, me and Mr. Mann just cut Sam Carter out a damn tree.
我和曼恩先生刚把山姆·卡特从树上割断了下来。


882
00:56:26.493 --> 00:56:27.828
Y'all hear me?
你们听见我说的了吗？


883
00:56:27.995 --> 00:56:30.747
Dirty, low-down bastards...
那些肮脏下流的混蛋...


884
00:56:30.914 --> 00:56:32.541
took my boy.
抓走了我的儿子。


885
00:56:32.749 --> 00:56:34.376
They got my cousin Aaron over in jail.
他们把我的表弟阿伦抓进了监狱。


886
00:56:34.543 --> 00:56:36.378
There's Sumner behind this business.
幕后的黑手就在萨姆纳。


887
00:56:36.545 --> 00:56:37.713
They say it's for his own protection.
他们说这是为了保护他。


888
00:56:37.921 --> 00:56:40.090
Now how that sound?
现在听上去会怎么样？


889
00:56:40.299 --> 00:56:42.718
What we need to do, we need to pray. Now, dear Lord...
我们需要做的，就是祈祷。现在,亲爱的主啊…


890
00:56:42.885 --> 00:56:45.095
I ain't in no praying mood,preacher.
我可没心情祈祷，牧师。


891
00:56:45.262 --> 00:56:46.847
Now, what I want to know is right now,
现在，我想知道的是，


892
00:56:47.014 --> 00:56:49.600
what y'all mens prepared to do if they run back here?
如果他们到这里来，你们准备怎么做?


893
00:56:49.808 --> 00:56:53.312
Not if, Sylvester. When.
不是如果，希尔维斯特，是何时。


894
00:56:53.479 --> 00:56:54.605
I'm goin' to shoot.
我就要开枪。


895
00:56:54.772 --> 00:56:56.857
Come on, sit down now, Big Baby.
算了吧，坐下，大宝贝。


896
00:57:04.239 --> 00:57:06.116
You by yourself there, Mr. Wright?
你就一个人来吗？赖特先生？


897
00:57:06.283 --> 00:57:07.701
I am, Sylvester.
我就一个人，希尔维斯特。


898
00:57:11.872 --> 00:57:14.625
Sylvester, them crackers so riled up,
希尔维斯特，他们被激怒了


899
00:57:14.792 --> 00:57:15.876
we don't know what they going to do.
我们不知道他们会怎么做。


900
00:57:16.043 --> 00:57:17.461
They don't know what they goin' to do.
他们不知道自己要做什么。


901
00:57:17.669 --> 00:57:19.630
That's how a lynch mob be.
这就是暴民滥用私刑的方式。


902
00:57:21.507 --> 00:57:24.259
Now, I say we send the women and children...
现在，要我说，我们把妇女儿童...


903
00:57:24.426 --> 00:57:26.720
to Gainesville right now.
立即送到盖恩斯维尔去。


904
00:57:26.887 --> 00:57:29.139
John, we can't go nowhere and leave that boy in jail.
约翰，我们不能把那孩子留在监狱里。


905
00:57:29.348 --> 00:57:31.558
No! Them dirty bastards...
不行！他们是肮脏的混蛋...


906
00:57:31.725 --> 00:57:34.061
can take my boy out of that jail...
会把我儿子劫持出监狱...


907
00:57:34.228 --> 00:57:36.772
and hang him whenever they take a notion.
然后随便就把他吊死。


908
00:57:36.939 --> 00:57:38.190
Don't worry about it, Uncle.
别着急，舅舅。


909
00:57:38.357 --> 00:57:40.567
We ain't going nowhere.
我们哪也不去。


910
00:57:40.734 --> 00:57:42.569
We ain't going nowhere, Bradley.
我们哪也不去，布莱德利。


911
00:57:42.736 --> 00:57:44.571
Now, we own this here land.
现在，我们拥有这片土地。


912
00:57:44.738 --> 00:57:46.657
We pay taxes on it.
我们为此纳税。


913
00:57:46.824 --> 00:57:48.325
Now, we don't bother nobody around here.
现在，我们不打扰这里的任何人。


914
00:57:48.492 --> 00:57:50.369
We keep to ourselves.
我们保持沉默。


915
00:57:50.536 --> 00:57:52.412
Now, colored folk just can't be running all the time.
现在，黑人不能总是逃跑啊。


916
00:57:52.579 --> 00:57:53.914
There comes a time when you got to stand up...
有时候你得站起来…


917
00:57:54.081 --> 00:57:55.082
and defend your rights.
捍卫你的权利。


918
00:57:55.249 --> 00:57:57.418
Sylvester! Sylvester! Listen to me. And you listen.
西尔维斯特!西尔维斯特!听我说。你听我说。


919
00:57:57.584 --> 00:57:58.836
Hold on there for a minute.
等一下。


920
00:57:59.002 --> 00:57:59.920
We got to think about these here children.
我们得为这些孩子着想。


921
00:58:00.087 --> 00:58:02.131
Oh, I am thinking about the children, preacher.
哦，我正在为这些孩子们考虑，牧师。


922
00:58:02.339 --> 00:58:05.384
Now, you suppose they thinking about our children?
现在，你认为他们在考虑我们的孩子吗?


923
00:58:12.850 --> 00:58:13.892
Mr. Mann.
曼恩先生。


924
00:58:17.229 --> 00:58:20.357
If there be some trouble around here, sir,
如果这里有什么麻烦，先生，


925
00:58:20.524 --> 00:58:22.443
we could sure use your help.
我们可能会需要你的帮助。


926
00:58:22.609 --> 00:58:25.487
I just came from one war, friend.
我刚从战场上下来，朋友。


927
00:58:25.654 --> 00:58:27.531
I ain't looking for another one.
我不想再找事了。


928
00:58:27.739 --> 00:58:29.616
Let him go, Sylvester.
让他走，西尔维斯特。


929
00:58:29.783 --> 00:58:31.118
For all we know,he could have been...
据我们所知，他可能是…


930
00:58:31.285 --> 00:58:32.369
the one that done this thing.
作案的元凶。


931
00:58:32.536 --> 00:58:34.830
They said it was... they said it was a stranger anyhow.
他们说那是…他们说那是个陌生人。


932
00:58:35.038 --> 00:58:37.291
You're talking crazy now, preacher.
你在说什么胡话，牧师。


933
00:58:42.671 --> 00:58:45.174
I wish y'all luck.
我祝愿大家都平安无事。


934
00:58:54.266 --> 00:58:55.684
He ain't done nothing.
他什么都没有做。


935
00:58:55.851 --> 00:58:58.070
What was that, Aunt Sarah?
那是怎么回事？萨拉阿姨？


936
00:59:00.898 --> 00:59:05.194
Mr. Wright, would you kindly excuse us, sir?
赖特先生，你能善意地回避一下我们的谈话吗？


937
00:59:16.538 --> 00:59:18.248
I seen his face.
我看见了那人的脸。


938
00:59:18.457 --> 00:59:20.250
He was white as butter.
那是一个典型的白人脸。


939
00:59:20.459 --> 00:59:22.795
What?
什么？


940
00:59:26.965 --> 00:59:30.177
This what they teach you in the Army?
这就他们在军队教你做的吗？


941
00:59:30.344 --> 00:59:33.680
Pack up and run when things get hot?
一碰上麻烦就收拾东西走人？


942
00:59:33.847 --> 00:59:35.224
Thank God the Navy don't let in...
感谢上帝，海军不会让...


943
00:59:35.390 --> 00:59:39.895
What? Go on and say it, Mr. Wright.
什么？接着说下去，赖特先生。


944
00:59:40.104 --> 00:59:43.232
Thank God the Navy don't let in niggers.
谢天谢地，海军从没有让黑鬼参加进来。


945
00:59:44.817 --> 00:59:46.902
I was going to say cowards.
我想说的是懦夫。


946
00:59:47.069 --> 00:59:48.946
That's right.I got you figured, Mann.
那就对了。我知道你的打算，曼恩。


947
00:59:49.113 --> 00:59:50.489
You one of them loud boys, big talk.
你也是个光说不练说大话的家伙。


948
00:59:50.656 --> 00:59:52.116
Figure you can say anything to a white man...
你可以对白人说任何话...


949
00:59:52.282 --> 00:59:54.618
as long as you start out saying,"With all due respect."
只要你以“恕我冒昧，”做开场白。


950
00:59:54.785 --> 00:59:57.246
First sign of trouble, you duckin' your head running.
一有麻烦，你就躲得远远的。


951
00:59:57.412 --> 00:59:58.914
What you going to do...
如果那些暴民来到这里...


952
00:59:59.081 --> 01:00:00.916
when that mob come down the road?
你将怎么办？


953
01:00:01.083 --> 01:00:02.501
You going to grab up your rifle,
你会拿起枪，


954
01:00:02.668 --> 01:00:03.961
defend colored folk?
来保卫黑人吗？


955
01:00:04.069 --> 01:00:05.479
What you care?
你在意什么？


956
01:00:05.546 --> 01:00:08.382
Man does what he has to.Ain't that right?
人总得为所在意的事情而做点什么，对吧？


957
01:00:08.549 --> 01:00:09.967
Just like a colored boy back from the war...
就像一个从战争中归来的黑人小伙子…


958
01:00:10.134 --> 01:00:11.510
with a pocketful of money.
带着一口袋钱。


959
01:00:11.677 --> 01:00:13.762
Ain't that right?
这合适吗？


960
01:00:13.929 --> 01:00:16.348
You the massa of Rosewood, huh?
你是紫檀镇的乡绅吧？


961
01:00:16.515 --> 01:00:17.474
Say, boy...
算是吧，孩子...


962
01:00:17.641 --> 01:00:18.976
these people know me.
这里的人都认识我。


963
01:00:19.143 --> 01:00:20.686
They trust me.
他们相信我。


964
01:00:27.234 --> 01:00:29.611
How long you live here, Mr. Wright?
你住在这里多久了？赖特先生


965
01:00:29.778 --> 01:00:31.655
Nine years.
九年了。


966
01:00:35.325 --> 01:00:38.203
I been in Rosewood one night...
我只在紫檀镇住了一晚...


967
01:00:38.370 --> 01:00:41.039
they asking me to stay.
他们要求我住下来。


968
01:00:41.206 --> 01:00:43.792
Now, you pack up your truck...
现在，你收拾好你的卡车…


969
01:00:44.001 --> 01:00:46.837
see who tries to stop you from leaving.
看看是谁试图阻止你离开。


970
01:01:08.859 --> 01:01:09.818
You wasn't going to say nothing.
你不会什么都不说吧。


971
01:01:09.985 --> 01:01:11.361
You was just going to leave me?
你就要离开我了吗？


972
01:01:11.528 --> 01:01:13.989
Three, four weeks, this all blow over.
三，四个星期后，这一切都过去了。


973
01:01:14.156 --> 01:01:15.449
Then I come back.
那时我再回来。


974
01:01:15.616 --> 01:01:17.993
But I thought we...
但我以为我们…


975
01:01:18.160 --> 01:01:21.163
Why, I didn't think you was just going to run off, is all.
我还以为你不是要跑掉呢。


976
01:01:21.330 --> 01:01:22.206
Ain't you a soldier?
你难道不是一名士兵吗？


977
01:01:22.372 --> 01:01:23.332
Scrappie.
斯卡比。


978
01:01:29.129 --> 01:01:30.672
Them boys looking for a colored man...
那些男人在找一个黑人…


979
01:01:30.839 --> 01:01:33.175
ain't nobody seen around here before.
以前没人在这附近见过的黑人。


980
01:01:33.342 --> 01:01:34.343
Now, ain't no way in the world...
现在，这世界上没有办法…


981
01:01:34.551 --> 01:01:37.012
one man got enough bullets for all them crackers.
一个人有足够的子弹对付他们。


982
01:01:37.179 --> 01:01:38.847
Your own preacher ready to serve me up.
你的牧师准备把我送上祭台。


983
01:01:39.014 --> 01:01:41.934
But if I stay,I'm asking to be hung.
但如果我留下，我就是在要求被绞死。


984
01:01:49.191 --> 01:01:50.234
Look here.
看这儿。


985
01:02:06.458 --> 01:02:09.086
They give me this for saving lives.
他们因为我救人而颁给我这个奖章。


986
01:02:11.755 --> 01:02:14.800
Most important thing anybody ever give to me.
这是别人给予我的最重要的东西。


987
01:02:14.967 --> 01:02:17.678
You keep it for me.
你替我保管它。


988
01:02:19.221 --> 01:02:22.141
Hold on to it till I get back.
收好它，直到我回来。


989
01:02:23.434 --> 01:02:25.936
Now, can you do that for me, darling?
现在，你能帮我个忙吗，亲爱的？


990
01:03:50.830 --> 01:03:54.830
星期六，阿内特的生日。

991
01:04:00.030 --> 01:04:01.698
Morning, Judge.
早上好，法官。


992
01:04:22.719 --> 01:04:26.223
Multiple gunshot wounds.
多处枪伤。


993
01:04:26.390 --> 01:04:28.392
Missing ear...
一只耳朵不见了...


994
01:04:29.560 --> 01:04:31.061
fingers...
手指不全...


995
01:04:32.563 --> 01:04:35.899
various other parts.
还有其他部分伤口。


996
01:04:36.066 --> 01:04:41.113
By Jesus, your boys really got to this one, huh, Ellis?
天啊，你的人也真够可以的，对吧？艾利斯。


997
01:04:45.033 --> 01:04:47.411
Yes, they did, sir.
是他们干的，先生。


998
01:04:53.709 --> 01:04:56.837
Levy County is growing.
李维县正在扩展。


999
01:04:57.004 --> 01:04:58.630
We need us a sheriff up here...
我们这里需要一个警长…


1000
01:04:58.797 --> 01:05:00.799
who can handle these nigger problems.
他要能处理这些黑鬼的事情。


1001
01:05:03.343 --> 01:05:05.012
Is that you, Ellis?
这会是你吗？艾利斯？


1002
01:05:05.179 --> 01:05:06.722
Now hold on, Judge.
等一下，法官。


1003
01:05:06.930 --> 01:05:10.976
Oh, I think I got everything under control now, Judge.
哦，我想现在一切都在掌控之中了，法官。


1004
01:05:11.143 --> 01:05:12.311
I hope so.
我希望如此。


1005
01:05:12.478 --> 01:05:13.979
We ain't talking about...
我们不是在说…


1006
01:05:14.104 --> 01:05:16.315
breaking up fights on Saturday night.
在周六晚上制止打架。


1007
01:05:16.482 --> 01:05:17.649
You can't control your colored,
你不能控制你治下的黑人，


1008
01:05:17.816 --> 01:05:20.569
we're going to replace you with someone who can.
我们就找个人来代替你。


1009
01:05:20.736 --> 01:05:21.570
Cause of death:
死因：


1010
01:05:21.779 --> 01:05:24.281
"Mischief at hands unknown..."
“恶作剧中失手致死...”


1011
01:05:24.490 --> 01:05:26.408
Write that down, Earl.
写下来，厄尔。


1012
01:05:26.658 --> 01:05:29.244
All right now!Get on in here!
全体注意！到这里来！


1013
01:05:29.411 --> 01:05:30.621
Fall in here, everybody!
大家来这里集合！


1014
01:05:30.829 --> 01:05:33.957
Now, hush up!
现在，都别废话！


1015
01:05:34.124 --> 01:05:37.086
Everybody, come on, now! Don't lollygag!
大家，快点! 别耽误功夫！


1016
01:05:37.252 --> 01:05:39.838
I want to give you a day off.
我今天要给你们放一天假。


1017
01:05:40.005 --> 01:05:41.090
What's that, Boots?
为了什么？布茨？


1018
01:05:42.424 --> 01:05:44.259
He says you got the day off.
他说，给你们一天的假。


1019
01:05:44.468 --> 01:05:45.594
All right!
好哇！


1020
01:05:45.803 --> 01:05:47.763
That colored boy what assaulted Fanny Taylor,
那个袭击范妮.泰勒的黑人男孩，


1021
01:05:47.930 --> 01:05:49.932
he's still out there somewhere.
他还逍遥法外。


1022
01:05:50.099 --> 01:05:51.517
So I'm gonna give you the day off...
所以我给你们放一天假...


1023
01:05:51.683 --> 01:05:53.644
so you can go help with the search.
这样你们可以协助搜查。


1024
01:05:53.811 --> 01:05:56.188
All I expect is...
我所希望的就是...


1025
01:05:56.355 --> 01:05:58.065
if you find him...
如果你们找到他...


1026
01:05:58.232 --> 01:06:00.258
well, you know what to do.
那你们，就自己看着办吧。


1027
01:06:16.039 --> 01:06:17.248
Oh, Lord, Auntie,
噢，上帝，阿姨，


1028
01:06:17.415 --> 01:06:19.667
they're likely to come in here and kill us all.
他们好像要闯到这里来杀我们了。


1029
01:06:19.834 --> 01:06:22.379
You got to tell them that man was white.
你得告诉他们那个人是个白人。


1030
01:06:22.545 --> 01:06:23.880
Child, you don't think...
孩子，你别想...


1031
01:06:24.047 --> 01:06:26.091
they going to listen to old Aunt Sarah?
他们会听萨拉老阿姨讲的话吗？


1032
01:06:26.257 --> 01:06:29.094
They'd just as soon as string me up...
他们只会马上把我绞死...


1033
01:06:29.260 --> 01:06:30.929
like they done Sam Carter.
就像他们对萨姆.卡特所干的。


1034
01:06:31.096 --> 01:06:35.892
You ain't never seen crackers act the way I know.
你从没见过那些坏蛋的行为，我知道。


1035
01:06:36.059 --> 01:06:39.562
When I was a little girl, about 7,
当我还是个大约7岁孩子时，


1036
01:06:39.729 --> 01:06:43.942
still on the Willowbrook plantation...
当时还在维罗布鲁克种植园...


1037
01:06:44.109 --> 01:06:50.657
old massa's son stole $20 out of the family chest...
老主人的儿子从家里的箱子里偷了20美元…


1038
01:06:50.824 --> 01:06:53.910
for a cockfight.
拿去斗鸡了。


1039
01:06:54.077 --> 01:06:55.995
Massa knew he took it.
主人知道是他儿子拿的。


1040
01:06:56.162 --> 01:07:00.625
As blue as Jesus' eyes, he knew.
就像他知道耶稣的眼睛是蓝色的。


1041
01:07:00.834 --> 01:07:04.462
But just the same...
但他还是...


1042
01:07:04.629 --> 01:07:08.758
he whipped my daddy half to death.
用鞭子把我爹抽了个半死不活。


1043
01:07:11.177 --> 01:07:15.765
It don't matter what man was beating on Fanny Taylor.
不管谁揍了范妮·泰勒。


1044
01:07:15.932 --> 01:07:18.059
Nigger.
黑人总是倒霉。


1045
01:07:18.226 --> 01:07:20.603
It's just another word for guilty.
只不过是有罪的另一种说法。


1046
01:07:26.192 --> 01:07:27.360
Here you go.
这是你的。


1047
01:07:27.527 --> 01:07:28.570
Thank you, Mr. Bryce.
谢谢你，布莱斯先生。


1048
01:07:28.737 --> 01:07:30.071
You're welcome.
不客气。


1049
01:07:30.238 --> 01:07:32.699
You're a nice gentleman.
你真是个大好人。


1050
01:07:34.617 --> 01:07:37.620
Look, why don't you get your peoples on board, Aunt Sarah?
为什么你不让你的人都上车呢？萨拉阿姨？


1051
01:07:37.829 --> 01:07:39.414
Take them up to Gainesville for a while.
带他们到盖恩斯维尔呆一阵。


1052
01:07:39.581 --> 01:07:41.249
Don't much like the looks of things around here.
我不太喜欢这里的情形。


1053
01:07:41.416 --> 01:07:42.459
Things been looking the same...
只要我还能记得住...


1054
01:07:42.625 --> 01:07:45.670
as long as I can remember, Mr. Bryce.
事情总是老样子，布莱斯先生。


1055
01:07:50.508 --> 01:07:52.177
You take care of yourself.
你自己多当心。


1056
01:07:55.555 --> 01:07:56.806
Take that.
接着。


1057
01:07:56.973 --> 01:07:58.224
Put it on the side there.
把它放在这边。


1058
01:07:58.391 --> 01:07:59.601
Board!
上车！


1059
01:08:15.575 --> 01:08:16.910
Sylvester?
西尔韦斯特？


1060
01:08:17.077 --> 01:08:19.037
- Go inside the depot, Mama.- Sylvester!
-你去仓库里。妈妈。 -西尔韦斯特！


1061
01:08:19.204 --> 01:08:20.413
Mama, it's all right.
妈妈，没事的。


1062
01:08:20.580 --> 01:08:21.539
Mama, go on.
妈妈，走啊。


1063
01:08:21.748 --> 01:08:23.375
Johnny.
约翰尼。


1064
01:08:23.583 --> 01:08:24.709
Sylvester!
西尔韦斯特！


1065
01:08:24.818 --> 01:08:26.978
Do you know the whereabouts of this Jesse Hunter?
你知道这个杰西·亨特的下落吗？


1066
01:08:27.087 --> 01:08:28.755
I do not.
我不知道。


1067
01:08:28.922 --> 01:08:30.757
You arrest that man who kill Sam Carter yet?
你们逮捕那个杀了山姆·卡特的人吗？


1068
01:08:30.924 --> 01:08:33.301
Don't you get uppity with me.
别对我这么傲慢。


1069
01:08:33.468 --> 01:08:35.178
I've come to warn you.
我来是警告你的。


1070
01:08:35.345 --> 01:08:36.471
There are some boys over there in Sumner...
萨姆纳那边有几个小伙子…


1071
01:08:36.638 --> 01:08:38.014
let on if they was you,
设想一下他们是你，


1072
01:08:38.181 --> 01:08:40.141
they wouldn't let sundown catch them around here.
他们不会等到太阳下山再来抓你的。


1073
01:08:40.308 --> 01:08:43.478
Well,they ain't me... sir.
但他们不是我...长官。


1074
01:08:47.607 --> 01:08:48.733
Why don't you be a good boy...
你为什么不做个好孩子…


1075
01:08:48.942 --> 01:08:50.735
and go visit some of your other relatives...
去拜访你的其他地方的亲戚…


1076
01:08:50.902 --> 01:08:52.195
for a little while, huh?
就在这几天，好吗？


1077
01:08:53.947 --> 01:08:56.449
I am trying to help you here.
我可是在帮你。


1078
01:08:57.951 --> 01:09:00.078
They're all over there right now getting all full of liquor...
他们现在都在那里喝得酩酊大醉…


1079
01:09:00.245 --> 01:09:02.664
and making nooses.
还在编绳套呢。


1080
01:09:03.665 --> 01:09:06.000
You hear me! Huh?
你就听我的话！好吗？


1081
01:09:06.167 --> 01:09:07.711
Sheriff...
治安官...


1082
01:09:07.919 --> 01:09:09.170
If you really want to help...
如果你真的想帮忙…


1083
01:09:09.337 --> 01:09:10.547
I appreciate it if you wouldn't allow...
就别让那帮小子来这儿，


1084
01:09:10.714 --> 01:09:13.675
them boys to come 'round here.
我会非常感激你的。


1085
01:09:13.842 --> 01:09:16.428
Now, I was born and raised in Rosewood.
我的出生和成长都在紫檀镇。


1086
01:09:16.636 --> 01:09:17.637
This here is my home.
这里是我的家。


1087
01:09:17.804 --> 01:09:21.015
And I'll be damned if I let anybody run me off it.
如果我被什么人赶走，那我也就死了。


1088
01:09:22.684 --> 01:09:24.719
Now, you can tell them boys that.
现在，你给那帮小子带个话。


1089
01:09:27.522 --> 01:09:30.575
Tell them your damn self.
你自己去告诉他们吧。


1090
01:09:32.777 --> 01:09:35.655
Damn colored fool.
该死的黑傻瓜。


1091
01:09:45.290 --> 01:09:46.558
Go home, Mama.
回家去，妈妈。


1092
01:09:52.623 --> 01:09:54.632
You're gonna have to settle your account...
你必须先把赊账结清...


1093
01:09:54.799 --> 01:09:57.093
before I can sell you the shells.
然后我再卖给你这些子弹。


1094
01:10:01.222 --> 01:10:03.016
Want me to settle the account?
想让我结清赊账？


1095
01:10:03.183 --> 01:10:04.726
That's right.
对了。


1096
01:10:05.894 --> 01:10:07.479
All right.
那好吧。


1097
01:10:09.022 --> 01:10:11.733
Go home, Jewel.
回家去，朱维尔。


1098
01:10:15.779 --> 01:10:17.864
Girl, you best get out of this store.
丫头，你最好离开这家店。


1099
01:10:18.031 --> 01:10:19.366
She belongs here.She belongs right here.
她属于这里，她就呆在这儿。


1100
01:10:19.532 --> 01:10:21.659
Do you see how you do my cousin?
你是都对我表妹干了些啥？


1101
01:10:21.826 --> 01:10:24.496
Get out this store right now, Jewel! Get!
快离开这家商店，朱维尔！快！


1102
01:10:25.814 --> 01:10:27.891
Can't you listen to nobody?
你就不能听听别人的话吗？


1103
01:10:27.957 --> 01:10:30.418
Sheriff give you good advice.Why ain't you leaving?
治安官给你忠告了。为啥你还不走？


1104
01:10:30.585 --> 01:10:32.587
I thought you a smart boy,Sylvester.
我认为你是聪明孩子，西尔维斯特。


1105
01:10:32.754 --> 01:10:34.805
I thought you a smart boy.
我想你脑子没病，孩子。


1106
01:10:35.590 --> 01:10:37.342
Here is your money,Mr. Wright.
这是你的钱，赖特先生。


1107
01:10:37.550 --> 01:10:40.720
That should settle my account.
应该够还清赊账了。


1108
01:10:40.887 --> 01:10:42.180
Sylvester...
西尔维斯特...


1109
01:10:42.347 --> 01:10:44.557
Dumb...
傻瓜...


1110
01:10:44.724 --> 01:10:45.925
Hurry up!
快走！


1111
01:10:50.939 --> 01:10:52.941
Here come them boys.
那些小伙子们来了。


1112
01:10:57.445 --> 01:10:59.230
They ain't got nothing.
他们什么都没找到。


1113
01:10:59.447 --> 01:11:00.782
What'd you find?
你们发现了什么？


1114
01:11:00.949 --> 01:11:02.492
Snakes and ticks.
竟是蛇和扁虱。


1115
01:11:02.701 --> 01:11:05.453
Them colored folks got to be hiding that nigger.
他的黑同胞一定把那黑鬼藏起来了。


1116
01:11:07.455 --> 01:11:08.790
What time is it,anyway?
现在几点了？


1117
01:11:08.957 --> 01:11:12.961
Well, let's see...by old Sam Carter.
好吧,让我们看看…老萨姆·卡特。


1118
01:11:14.963 --> 01:11:17.465
Bourbon time.
该喝波旁酒了。


1119
01:11:19.718 --> 01:11:21.678
I'll tell you, boys.
我跟你们说，小伙子们。


1120
01:11:21.845 --> 01:11:23.430
If anybody's hiding Jesse Hunter,
如果有人把杰西·亨特藏起来


1121
01:11:23.596 --> 01:11:25.573
my money's on Sylvester Carrier.
我把赌注押在西尔维斯特.凯利上。


1122
01:11:25.640 --> 01:11:27.726
That nigger,he hates us white folk.
那个黑鬼，他恨我们这些白人。


1123
01:11:27.892 --> 01:11:28.893
He does.
他是的。


1124
01:11:29.060 --> 01:11:30.854
You know,he's got a piano.
你们知道，他有架钢琴。


1125
01:11:31.062 --> 01:11:33.523
A nigger with a goddamn piano.
一个黑鬼居然他妈的还有钢琴。


1126
01:11:33.690 --> 01:11:35.567
I've been working all my life,
我工作了一辈子，


1127
01:11:35.734 --> 01:11:37.610
I ain't got a piano.
却没有钢琴。


1128
01:11:37.777 --> 01:11:39.821
You don't know how to play one.
你都不知道该怎么弹。


1129
01:11:39.988 --> 01:11:41.114
That ain't the point.
这不是重点。


1130
01:11:41.281 --> 01:11:43.742
Old man Cummer,up in that house of his,
坎默老伙计，就在他房里，


1131
01:11:43.908 --> 01:11:45.326
he's got a piano.
居然摆着一架钢琴。


1132
01:11:45.493 --> 01:11:48.038
That nigger's got one,and I don't.
黑鬼有，我却没有。


1133
01:11:48.246 --> 01:11:49.205
Now, how does that look?
这像话吗？


1134
01:11:49.414 --> 01:11:51.332
Yeah, and he's married to that white woman.
是啊，他还娶了那个白人女人。


1135
01:11:51.499 --> 01:11:52.625
Gertrude ain't white.
格特鲁德不是白人。


1136
01:11:52.792 --> 01:11:53.935
Hell, she look white.
见鬼，她看上去像白人。


1137
01:11:54.002 --> 01:11:55.086
Well, she ain't.
那她也不是。


1138
01:11:55.253 --> 01:11:58.757
She's half Negress,half-Seminole Indian.
她一半黑人，一半塞米诺印第安血统。


1139
01:11:58.923 --> 01:11:59.883
He says.
他说的。


1140
01:12:00.050 --> 01:12:02.677
It wouldn't surprise me if he was hiding that bastard.
我一点儿都不奇怪他藏了那个混蛋。


1141
01:12:02.844 --> 01:12:04.429
Hey, Judge.
嘿，法官大人。


1142
01:12:13.563 --> 01:12:14.773
I tell you, Duke.
我告诉你，杜克。


1143
01:12:14.939 --> 01:12:16.566
Can I get that bottle?
把那瓶给我喝一口吧？


1144
01:12:40.173 --> 01:12:41.591
Go ahead now,make a wish.
接下来，许个愿。


1145
01:12:43.218 --> 01:12:44.969
Blow the candles out.
吹蜡烛。


1146
01:12:51.643 --> 01:12:53.561
Open this one first, Arnett.Open that one.
先把这个打开，阿内特。打开。


1147
01:13:03.905 --> 01:13:06.199
Oh, yeah,that's nice, Mama.
哦，这个很好，妈妈。


1148
01:13:06.366 --> 01:13:07.659
Yeah, that's real nice.
这真的很好。


1149
01:13:07.826 --> 01:13:10.887
You're a man now.You need a suit of clothes.
你现在是男人了，该有一身合适的衣服了。


1150
01:13:22.173 --> 01:13:26.052
Arnett, open this one here and that one, too.
阿内特，把这个打开，那个也打开。


1151
01:13:26.219 --> 01:13:28.805
Sylvester got that one.
西尔维斯特送的那个。


1152
01:13:40.158 --> 01:13:42.268
Simmer down.Be quiet!
冷静一下，别出声！


1153
01:13:46.406 --> 01:13:49.576
Sylvester, come on out here now, boy.
西尔维斯特，你小子出来。


1154
01:13:49.743 --> 01:13:50.952
We want to talk to you.
俺们有话跟你说。


1155
01:13:51.119 --> 01:13:53.580
Bring that Jesse Hunter on out here with you.
你把杰西.亨特交出来。


1156
01:13:53.747 --> 01:13:55.790
Yeah, that's right.Bring that boy with you.
没错，把那小子带出来。


1157
01:13:55.999 --> 01:13:58.001
Jesse and Sylvester are probably sitting up in there.
杰西和希尔维斯特可能就在里面。


1158
01:13:58.209 --> 01:13:59.836
Shut up that damn dog.
别让那该死的狗叫了。


1159
01:14:00.045 --> 01:14:02.630
Sittin' up there now eating pork chops.
扔块排骨让它啃着。


1160
01:14:02.797 --> 01:14:04.257
Laughing at us all.
不把俺们当回事儿。


1161
01:14:04.424 --> 01:14:05.508
Goddamn, Duke!
该死，杜克！


1162
01:14:07.010 --> 01:14:09.471
Son of a...
王八蛋...


1163
01:14:10.513 --> 01:14:11.681
You had no call to do that.
你没必要这么做。


1164
01:14:11.790 --> 01:14:13.241
It's just a damn dog,Ellis.
只不过是一条该死的狗，艾利斯。


1165
01:14:13.308 --> 01:14:14.617
I'll have no more shooting.
不许再开枪了。


1166
01:14:14.684 --> 01:14:15.810
How you expect the boy to come out here...
你都把他的狗打死了...


1167
01:14:15.977 --> 01:14:17.395
if you're going to shoot his hound?
怎么能指望这小子出来?


1168
01:14:17.562 --> 01:14:19.230
Hell of a shot!
打得好！


1169
01:14:19.397 --> 01:14:21.858
Sylvester! You'd better get out here now.
西尔维斯特！你最好现在就出来。


1170
01:14:23.985 --> 01:14:25.612
Wait, Mama!Mama, hold on!
等一下，妈妈！别动！


1171
01:14:26.905 --> 01:14:28.907
Get out the window, Mama.
离开窗户，妈妈。


1172
01:14:32.827 --> 01:14:34.662
All right. I'm gonna go get the guns, Mama.
好吧，妈妈，我去拿枪。


1173
01:14:34.829 --> 01:14:35.789
You stay out the window.
你离开窗户。


1174
01:14:35.955 --> 01:14:37.290
No, Sylvester!
不，西尔维斯特！


1175
01:14:37.457 --> 01:14:38.500
Mama, just stay out the window.
妈妈，离开窗户。


1176
01:14:38.666 --> 01:14:40.794
Y'all children get down right now.
孩子们都给我趴下来。


1177
01:14:40.960 --> 01:14:42.312
Get down under the table right now.
现在全都躲到桌子底下去。


1178
01:14:42.420 --> 01:14:43.980
Scrappie, Gertie,you keep these kids down.
斯卡比，格蒂，你俩照顾好孩子们。


1179
01:14:44.089 --> 01:14:45.965
Big Baby, get down! Get down!
大宝贝，趴下！趴下！


1180
01:15:05.694 --> 01:15:08.363
We don't want to talk to you.We want to talk to your boy.
俺们不想跟你说。俺们想跟你儿子讲话。


1181
01:15:08.530 --> 01:15:10.407
Boys, why don't y'all go on home?
孩子们，你们为什么不在家呆着？


1182
01:15:10.573 --> 01:15:12.450
Miz Sarah, we want to talk to Sylvester.
萨拉女士，俺们想找西尔维斯特。


1183
01:15:12.617 --> 01:15:15.286
You get him out here!Right now!
你让他出来！马上！


1184
01:15:15.453 --> 01:15:19.124
Mr. Walker, my boy don't know nothing about this business.
沃克先生，我儿子对这事一无所知。


1185
01:15:19.290 --> 01:15:20.517
You let him tell us that.
你让他跟俺们讲。


1186
01:15:20.583 --> 01:15:22.268
Let Jesse Hunter tell us something.
让杰西·亨特跟俺们讲。


1187
01:15:22.335 --> 01:15:24.838
Boys, I know y'all.
孩子们，我认识你们每一个人。


1188
01:15:25.004 --> 01:15:27.048
I was midwife to more than half of you...
你们中有一半都是我接生的...


1189
01:15:27.215 --> 01:15:28.591
and some of your young ones.
还有你们自己的孩子。


1190
01:15:28.800 --> 01:15:30.051
Bring that boy out here now!
让那小子出来！


1191
01:15:30.218 --> 01:15:33.471
I done seen you come up from babies to now.
我看到你从婴儿成长到现在。


1192
01:15:33.638 --> 01:15:35.765
Ain't nothing going to come of this.
这事不该是这个样子的。


1193
01:15:35.974 --> 01:15:38.017
It don't make sense.
这没道理啊。


1194
01:15:38.184 --> 01:15:40.562
My Sylvester ain't had nothing to do with this mess.
我的希尔维斯特跟这事一点关系都没有。


1195
01:15:40.729 --> 01:15:45.400
We ain't never known no Jesse Hunter.
我们根本不认识什么杰西·亨特。


1196
01:15:45.567 --> 01:15:48.069
I was there with Miss Fanny.
我当时和范妮小姐在一起。


1197
01:15:48.278 --> 01:15:51.740
I seen the man's face as plain as day.
我在光天化日下看清了那人的脸。


1198
01:15:51.948 --> 01:15:55.326
And most of you mens know that that man was white!
他和你们大多数人一样，是个白人！


1199
01:16:02.167 --> 01:16:03.460
Who fired that shot?
谁开的枪？


1200
01:16:03.626 --> 01:16:05.045
You tell me right now.
你们回答我。


1201
01:16:05.211 --> 01:16:06.604
I told you no more shooting.
我说过了，不许再开枪。


1202
01:16:06.671 --> 01:16:08.673
Didn't I tell you that?
我没告诉过你们吗？


1203
01:16:18.933 --> 01:16:20.393
Aunt Sarah.
萨拉阿姨。


1204
01:16:37.577 --> 01:16:38.703
Poly, get back here!
波利，回来！


1205
01:16:38.870 --> 01:16:39.788
Shut up, Walker.
闭嘴，沃克。


1206
01:16:39.954 --> 01:16:41.389
Quit squealing like a stuck pig.
别像杀猪叫了。


1207
01:16:41.456 --> 01:16:43.266
I'll take this boy out myself.
我要亲自把这小子弄出来。


1208
01:16:43.375 --> 01:16:44.918
Damn you,get back here!
你该死，回来！


1209
01:16:56.638 --> 01:16:59.057
Pledge your souls to hell!
让你的灵魂下地狱吧！


1210
01:17:29.629 --> 01:17:32.340
Get back under there.Stay there! Stay down!
回到下面去。呆在那儿!趴着别动！


1211
01:17:41.933 --> 01:17:44.436
Get inside, son.Go on inside.
进屋去，儿子，进屋去。


1212
01:17:47.147 --> 01:17:48.982
Hold your fire!
停止射击！


1213
01:17:49.149 --> 01:17:49.983
Hold your fire!
停止射击！


1214
01:17:50.150 --> 01:17:51.167
Think we got him?
我们打中他了？


1215
01:17:51.234 --> 01:17:52.168
I don't know.
我不知道。


1216
01:17:52.235 --> 01:17:53.445
We gonna need more bullets.
俺们需要更多子弹。


1217
01:17:53.611 --> 01:17:54.946
You go and tell,
你快去，


1218
01:17:55.113 --> 01:17:56.239
tell the judge what happened here.
告诉法官这里发生的事情。


1219
01:17:56.448 --> 01:17:58.158
Go!
去！


1220
01:17:58.324 --> 01:18:02.370
Rest of y'all men, get back!Go on. Stay low.
其余的人退后！快，低着点儿走。


1221
01:18:11.379 --> 01:18:12.797
I'm right here.
我在这儿。


1222
01:18:12.964 --> 01:18:14.591
I'm right here, Mama.
我在这儿呢，妈妈。


1223
01:18:14.799 --> 01:18:17.385
Hold on!
挺住！


1224
01:18:17.552 --> 01:18:20.555
Hold on, OK, Mama? I'm right here.
妈妈坚持住，好吗？我就在这儿。


1225
01:18:25.518 --> 01:18:27.979
Don't try to talk,Mama, don't try to talk.
别说话，妈妈，别试着说话。


1226
01:18:35.487 --> 01:18:37.197
Don't...
别...


1227
01:18:38.656 --> 01:18:43.244
Don't let them s-s-surround you, baby.
别让他们包围你，宝贝。


1228
01:18:43.411 --> 01:18:44.746
It's all right.I won't, Mama.
没事了。我不会的，妈妈。


1229
01:18:44.913 --> 01:18:46.164
You just hold on, OK?
你只要挺住，行吗？


1230
01:18:46.331 --> 01:18:48.416
Mama, no, hold on.
妈妈，不，挺住。


1231
01:18:48.583 --> 01:18:51.294
Mama, hold on.
妈妈，挺住。


1232
01:18:51.503 --> 01:18:53.296
Mama, hold on.
妈妈，挺住。


1233
01:19:21.533 --> 01:19:23.576
Y'all take what you need and no more!
你们全都要拿，已经没货了！


1234
01:19:23.743 --> 01:19:25.704
You hear me?
你们听见我说的了吗？


1235
01:19:25.870 --> 01:19:27.497
Y'all hear me?
你们都听见我说的了吗？


1236
01:19:29.999 --> 01:19:32.293
How am I going to be paid for all this?
怎么要我付出这么多?


1237
01:19:33.712 --> 01:19:35.880
You just keep track,that's all.
你只要记账就行了。


1238
01:19:38.758 --> 01:19:42.387
Y'all shoot Sylvester,Ellis?
你们都向西尔维斯特开枪了？艾利斯？


1239
01:19:42.554 --> 01:19:43.972
Don't know.
不太清楚。


1240
01:19:45.473 --> 01:19:47.517
They shot Aunt Sarah,though, John.
但他们还是射杀了萨拉阿姨，约翰。


1241
01:19:49.185 --> 01:19:50.478
Aunt Sarah!
萨拉阿姨！


1242
01:19:52.063 --> 01:19:54.190
What the hell's the matter with you, Ellis?
你这是怎么回事啊？艾利斯？


1243
01:19:54.357 --> 01:19:56.317
You let them come here and shoot an old woman?
你怎么让他们随便就打死一个老太太？


1244
01:19:56.484 --> 01:19:57.902
I didn't let them do that.
我没让他们这么做。


1245
01:19:58.069 --> 01:20:00.155
You call that upholding the law?
你就是这样维护法律的吗？


1246
01:20:00.321 --> 01:20:02.365
What kind of sheriff are you?
你算哪门子治安官啊？


1247
01:20:04.993 --> 01:20:08.538
Henry and Poly are dead.
亨利和波利死了。


1248
01:20:15.837 --> 01:20:18.339
Shot by them damn nigras.
被那该死的黑鬼打死的。


1249
01:20:21.176 --> 01:20:24.311
Where'd Sylvester get his ammunition, John?
约翰，西尔维斯特从哪儿搞来的弹药？


1250
01:20:37.817 --> 01:20:38.818
All right, come on.
没事了，来吧。


1251
01:20:38.985 --> 01:20:40.362
Come on. Hurry up! Hurry up!
来吧。快点！快点！


1252
01:20:40.528 --> 01:20:41.863
Come on! Come on!
来吧！来吧！


1253
01:20:42.706 --> 01:20:44.716
Take those babies,go hide in the woods.
带着这些孩子们躲进树林里。


1254
01:20:44.783 --> 01:20:46.117
Y'all babies going to get in the woods now.
孩子们，你们都到树林里去。


1255
01:20:46.284 --> 01:20:48.119
Go on!Go hide in the woods.
去吧！去树林里躲好。


1256
01:20:48.286 --> 01:20:50.789
Go on. Hurry up.Go hide in the woods.
快去树林里躲好。


1257
01:20:50.955 --> 01:20:52.123
Sylvester,I ain't leaving you.
西尔韦斯特，我不离开你。


1258
01:20:52.290 --> 01:20:53.391
Gertie, they gonna come back here...
葛蒂。那帮家伙还会回来的...


1259
01:20:53.458 --> 01:20:54.876
and try to kill all of us.
他们想杀了我们。


1260
01:20:55.043 --> 01:20:56.586
You and Scrappie got to go hide these children in the swamp.
你和斯卡比必须带孩子们躲进沼泽地里。


1261
01:20:56.695 --> 01:20:58.480
We can't take the babies out there. It's freezing!
我们不能让孩子们去那里。太冷了！


1262
01:20:58.546 --> 01:21:00.632
There ain't no place else.Go on and get out of here.
没有其它地方可去了。赶紧离开这里。


1263
01:21:00.799 --> 01:21:01.758
What about Aunt Sarah?
萨拉阿姨怎么办？


1264
01:21:01.925 --> 01:21:03.551
Just go on and get, girl!
只要离开就行，姑娘们！


1265
01:21:03.718 --> 01:21:05.470
Come on. Let's go.
来吧，我们走。


1266
01:21:10.266 --> 01:21:12.268
Gertie. I'll be there.
葛蒂，我回去找你们的。


1267
01:21:12.435 --> 01:21:14.896
You got to go. You got to go.
你们得走。你们得走。


1268
01:21:20.068 --> 01:21:21.569
Come on,Big Baby, get!
快去，大宝贝，走！


1269
01:21:23.655 --> 01:21:26.157
I can shoot,Sylvester.
我能开枪，西尔韦斯特。


1270
01:21:27.659 --> 01:21:29.953
Big Baby gonna shoot.
大宝贝要开枪。


1271
01:21:34.374 --> 01:21:35.750
All right.
好吧。


1272
01:21:37.585 --> 01:21:39.087
All right. Come on.
好吧。来吧。


1273
01:21:39.254 --> 01:21:40.338
How many are there in the house?
屋子里有多少人？


1274
01:21:40.505 --> 01:21:43.299
Sylvester, Jesse Hunter, James Carrier.
西尔韦斯特，詹姆斯.亨特，詹姆斯.凯利。


1275
01:21:43.508 --> 01:21:44.676
Probably that drifter.
也许还有那个流浪汉。


1276
01:21:44.843 --> 01:21:46.344
Yeah, Rodney. Listen.
好吧，罗德尼。听着。


1277
01:21:46.511 --> 01:21:47.971
You get together all the men you can find...
你把所有你能找到的男人聚在一起…


1278
01:21:48.138 --> 01:21:49.597
and you hightail it to Sumner.
你们速来萨姆纳。


1279
01:21:49.764 --> 01:21:51.266
Now, you make sure they bring rifles.
你要确保他们带着步枪。


1280
01:21:51.433 --> 01:21:52.367
What happened?
咋了？


1281
01:21:52.434 --> 01:21:54.144
Three dead white men is all.
有三个白人死了。


1282
01:21:54.310 --> 01:21:57.981
We done got ourselves a goddamn nigger revolt up here.
我们已经惹上了一场该死的黑鬼暴乱。


1283
01:22:10.785 --> 01:22:12.495
Hold your fire!
不要开枪！


1284
01:22:15.248 --> 01:22:16.708
There he is!
他又来了！


1285
01:22:27.093 --> 01:22:28.094
I think I got him!
我想我打中他了！


1286
01:22:28.261 --> 01:22:29.387
Hold your fire!
停火！


1287
01:22:33.141 --> 01:22:34.309
Goddamn you!
去你妈的！


1288
01:22:34.476 --> 01:22:36.478
Burn!
烧了它！


1289
01:22:38.521 --> 01:22:40.231
Light 'em up!
点燃它！


1290
01:22:58.083 --> 01:23:02.170
Some of y'all pick Henry and Poly up.
你们几个给亨利和波利收尸。


1291
01:23:18.687 --> 01:23:20.188
That Sylvester?
那是西尔韦斯特？


1292
01:23:26.027 --> 01:23:27.487
You son of a bitch!
你个王八蛋！


1293
01:24:05.191 --> 01:24:06.901
You want me to burn her, too?
你想让俺把她也烧了吗？


1294
01:24:09.946 --> 01:24:12.657
Couple y'all men,come over here.
过来几个人。


1295
01:24:14.826 --> 01:24:18.288
I want y'all to carry her down to the nigger graveyard.
我要你们把她抬到黑鬼墓地去。


1296
01:24:21.666 --> 01:24:23.752
Go on!
去吧！


1297
01:24:23.918 --> 01:24:26.713
I'll do it if you make me deputy.
如果你让俺当副警长，俺就去。


1298
01:24:26.880 --> 01:24:28.965
You're deputy now.
你现在就是副警长了。


1299
01:24:29.174 --> 01:24:30.675
Go on, pick her up.
去吧，给她入殓。


1300
01:24:30.842 --> 01:24:33.470
Hey, boys,I'm a deputy!
嘿，伙计们，俺现在是副警长了！


1301
01:24:35.472 --> 01:24:37.632
Hold on to that now. Grab the other side.
现在抬起这头。抓住那头。


1302
01:24:37.640 --> 01:24:40.060
Hold on, Bobby.Hold on.
等一下，波比。等一下。


1303
01:24:42.854 --> 01:24:44.814
This wasn't supposed to happen.
这是不应该发生的。


1304
01:24:47.150 --> 01:24:49.527
She worked in my damn house, Ellis.
她在我家工作，艾利斯。


1305
01:24:55.784 --> 01:24:58.453
Then give her a decent Christian burial, James.
那就给她一个体面的基督徒葬礼，詹姆斯。


1306
01:25:09.297 --> 01:25:12.050
You men, grab that end.
你们几个，抓住那头。


1307
01:25:12.217 --> 01:25:14.511
Damn, what did this old crow eat?
该死，这只老乌鸦都吃了什么？


1308
01:25:14.719 --> 01:25:16.846
Come on, lift it up!
来吧，抬起来！


1309
01:25:22.644 --> 01:25:24.729
Look out now! Look out!
小心脚下了！小心！


1310
01:26:11.943 --> 01:26:14.779
Aunt Sarah come in the morning.
萨拉阿姨早上会来的。


1311
01:26:14.946 --> 01:26:16.448
She clean up.
她来收拾房间。


1312
01:26:16.614 --> 01:26:17.615
Aunt Sarah ain't coming.
萨拉阿姨不来了。


1313
01:26:18.950 --> 01:26:20.785
No. You right.
是的，你说对了。


1314
01:26:21.953 --> 01:26:23.872
It's Sunday.
今儿是礼拜天。


1315
01:26:24.039 --> 01:26:27.751
Aunt Sarah ain't comin' no more.
萨拉阿姨不会再来了。


1316
01:26:31.004 --> 01:26:32.422
No more, no never.
永远不会再来了。


1317
01:26:34.924 --> 01:26:36.009
She's dead.
她死了。


1318
01:26:41.473 --> 01:26:43.975
Sylvester, too,dead as hell.
西尔韦斯特也进地狱了。


1319
01:26:47.479 --> 01:26:48.772
Sam Carter.
同萨姆.卡特一样。


1320
01:26:53.985 --> 01:26:55.320
Half of Rosewood's dead,
紫檀镇上一半的都死了，


1321
01:26:55.487 --> 01:26:58.490
and they ain't caught your nigger yet!
他们还没抓到强奸你的那个黑鬼！


1322
01:26:59.949 --> 01:27:02.160
Sarah...
萨拉...


1323
01:27:03.370 --> 01:27:05.288
Sarah...
萨拉...


1324
01:27:08.500 --> 01:27:11.252
Why they hurt that old woman?
他们为什么要伤害那个老大妈？


1325
01:27:13.505 --> 01:27:16.132
She never done nothin'to nobody.
她谁都没得罪过。


1326
01:27:36.332 --> 01:27:39.332
星期天

1327
01:28:07.976 --> 01:28:10.562
Y'all need to come on down here.
你们都过来一下。


1328
01:28:10.729 --> 01:28:11.813
We're gonna need some help.
俺们需要一些帮助。


1329
01:28:11.980 --> 01:28:13.773
Some colored beat and raped a white girl.
一些黑人在袭击并强奸一位白人妇女。


1330
01:28:13.940 --> 01:28:15.025
Yeah, them niggers need to be put in their place.
是啊，那些黑鬼应该被赶回他们来的地方。


1331
01:28:15.191 --> 01:28:16.818
Hell, they done forgot who they are.
见鬼，他们已经忘了他们是什么。


1332
01:28:16.985 --> 01:28:17.986
I'm gonna get me one.
俺也要去杀一个。


1333
01:28:18.153 --> 01:28:20.196
We're gonna string up all them darkies.
俺们要把那些黑人都吊起来。


1334
01:28:20.363 --> 01:28:24.117
Yes, we'll gather at the river
是的，我们齐聚河边


1335
01:28:24.284 --> 01:28:28.872
The beautiful,the beautiful river
这是一条美丽的河流


1336
01:28:29.080 --> 01:28:33.376
Gather with the saints at the river
汇集了圣徒们的河流


1337
01:28:33.543 --> 01:28:34.419
That flows...
那些花朵...


1338
01:28:34.586 --> 01:28:36.437
Y'all hear what happened in Rosewood?
你们都听说了紫檀镇上发生的事情了吧？


1339
01:28:36.504 --> 01:28:37.839
A colored boy killed four white men...
一个黑人小伙子杀死个白人男子...


1340
01:28:38.006 --> 01:28:39.716
and raped three white women.
还强奸了三名白人妇女。


1341
01:28:39.924 --> 01:28:42.886
Soon we'll reach the shining river
很快我们将到达闪光的河流


1342
01:28:43.053 --> 01:28:47.265
Soon our pilgrimage will cease
很快我们的朝拜就要结束


1343
01:28:47.432 --> 01:28:51.186
Soon our happy hearts will quiver
很快我们的心灵将会颤抖


1344
01:28:51.353 --> 01:28:55.815
With the melody of peace
带着此刻和平的旋律


1345
01:28:55.982 --> 01:29:00.528
Yes, we'll gather at the river
是的，我们齐聚河边


1346
01:29:00.695 --> 01:29:03.990
The beautiful,the beautiful river...
这条美丽的河流...


1347
01:29:04.157 --> 01:29:05.283
Right over there!
看那儿！


1348
01:29:05.450 --> 01:29:06.785
There he is!Get him!
就是他！抓住他！


1349
01:29:06.951 --> 01:29:08.411
On that horse!Give me my gun!
他骑着马！把枪给俺！


1350
01:29:28.181 --> 01:29:31.226
Jesse! You were better off on that chain gang, boy!
杰西！你最好就被锁着，小子！


1351
01:29:31.393 --> 01:29:32.811
There he is!
他在那里！


1352
01:29:47.158 --> 01:29:49.411
Let's go, boys!Come on! Get him!
我们上！小伙子们！来吧！抓住他！


1353
01:29:55.500 --> 01:29:56.559
Move it!
快撤！


1354
01:29:56.668 --> 01:29:58.128
Let's get out of here.
离开这儿。


1355
01:30:08.555 --> 01:30:09.889
Drop that gun!
把枪收起来了！


1356
01:30:10.056 --> 01:30:11.599
Get them horses out of here!
别把他们的马惊了！


1357
01:30:11.766 --> 01:30:13.977
Hey, you hold that horse down!
嘿，你拴住那匹马！


1358
01:30:14.144 --> 01:30:15.520
Now, get him on over there!
现在，把他弄到那边去！


1359
01:30:15.687 --> 01:30:17.522
Go on!
快去！


1360
01:30:17.689 --> 01:30:19.290
Oh, Ellis,let 'em run!
哦，艾利斯，让他们跑起来！


1361
01:30:19.357 --> 01:30:21.417
Let 'em run! Howdy-do!
让他们跑起来！都好吗！


1362
01:30:27.532 --> 01:30:28.992
Ooh, here come the parade.
我操，游行开始了。


1363
01:30:32.162 --> 01:30:35.123
Hey, listen up! Come on! Come on over here!
嘿，听着！过来！都到这边来！


1364
01:30:35.331 --> 01:30:36.391
Come on!
来吧！


1365
01:30:36.499 --> 01:30:39.377
15 niggers jumped us in the woods!

1366
01:30:39.544 --> 01:30:41.212
They was armed to the teeth!
他们都武装到了牙齿！


1367
01:30:41.379 --> 01:30:43.506
What? They bump you in the head?
怎么了？他们打肿你的头啦？


1368
01:30:43.673 --> 01:30:44.674
Sure enough did!
绝对是他们干的！


1369
01:30:44.841 --> 01:30:45.842
You go on and get them, then!
那你应该去把他们抓住！


1370
01:30:46.051 --> 01:30:46.885
Let's all get 'em!
让俺们一起去抓他们！


1371
01:30:47.052 --> 01:30:48.736
- Was it back there?- Back yonder.
-是在后面吗？-就在那后面。


1372
01:30:48.803 --> 01:30:50.680
Go now!
立刻出发！


1373
01:30:57.395 --> 01:31:00.231
Hey, Ellis, you got a phone call, Ellis.
嘿，艾利斯，有电话找你，艾利斯。


1374
01:31:00.398 --> 01:31:02.817
Not now, Earl!
现在不接，厄尔！


1375
01:31:02.984 --> 01:31:04.819
It's the governor, Ellis.
是州长打来的，艾利斯。


1376
01:31:09.407 --> 01:31:11.326
Pretty exciting stuff,huh, Ellis?
挺挺刺激吧？埃利斯？


1377
01:31:24.089 --> 01:31:26.049
Go right inside, Timothy.
进屋去，蒂莫西。


1378
01:31:35.600 --> 01:31:36.643
See the nigger?They got him.
看见那黑鬼了吗？他们抓到他了。


1379
01:31:36.810 --> 01:31:38.019
No. You've got to look and see.
不，你得睁眼看着这些。


1380
01:31:38.228 --> 01:31:39.646
You've got to remember this.
你要记住这些。


1381
01:31:39.813 --> 01:31:41.398
It's somethin' you've got to remember. Look.
这是你必须要记住的。看呀。


1382
01:32:06.339 --> 01:32:08.466
What? What?
怎么了？发生什么？


1383
01:32:16.975 --> 01:32:20.311
Mr. Wright,you have to hide me.
赖特先生，你得把我藏起来。


1384
01:32:20.478 --> 01:32:22.313
You are crazy.
你疯了。


1385
01:32:22.480 --> 01:32:23.815
I can't run.
我不能跑了。


1386
01:32:23.982 --> 01:32:27.318
Mr. Wright, I don't know where my boys are,
赖特先生，我不知道我的儿子在哪里，


1387
01:32:27.485 --> 01:32:30.822
and my baby girl is somewhere...
而我的宝贝女儿在...


1388
01:32:30.989 --> 01:32:32.657
in the woods.
树林里。


1389
01:32:35.994 --> 01:32:37.328
Mr. Wright...
赖特先生...


1390
01:32:39.330 --> 01:32:41.791
they killed my Virginia.
他们杀了我的弗吉尼亚。


1391
01:32:47.106 --> 01:32:50.191
They find you here,they'll burn my store.
如果他们发现你在这里，他们会烧了我的店。


1392
01:32:50.258 --> 01:32:52.385
You best run hide in the woods.
你最好也躲进树林里。


1393
01:32:52.552 --> 01:32:54.637
I can't run!
我跑不动！


1394
01:32:54.846 --> 01:32:58.433
I got shot through my side.
我中枪了。


1395
01:33:03.271 --> 01:33:05.815
I can pay you.
我可以给你付钱。


1396
01:33:14.991 --> 01:33:17.744
We'll put you in the back storeroom.
我们会把你放在后面的储藏室。


1397
01:33:17.911 --> 01:33:19.329
Thank you.
谢谢你。


1398
01:33:19.496 --> 01:33:22.332
We'll talk about that deed later, Bradley.
我们以后再谈钱的事，布拉德利。


1399
01:33:22.499 --> 01:33:24.501
God bless you,John Wright.
上帝保佑你，约翰.赖特。


1400
01:33:30.465 --> 01:33:33.343
Get some clean white rags, blanket.
拿些干净的白纱布，还有毯子。


1401
01:33:43.019 --> 01:33:44.354
Here they come.
他们来了。


1402
01:33:44.521 --> 01:33:46.356
What are you fellas doing in the road?
你们这帮家伙挡在路上作甚？


1403
01:33:46.523 --> 01:33:47.357
Hold steady, boys.
小子们，保持镇定。


1404
01:33:47.524 --> 01:33:48.983
You can back up right now!
你们现在可以后退了！


1405
01:33:49.192 --> 01:33:50.360
Move them trucks out!
把卡车挪开！


1406
01:33:50.527 --> 01:33:51.986
Come on!
快点儿！


1407
01:33:53.405 --> 01:33:55.532
You know what to do now.
你们知道该怎么做。


1408
01:33:55.740 --> 01:33:57.283
We got business to take care of!
我们还有事要做！


1409
01:33:57.450 --> 01:33:58.326
OK, now...
好了，现在...


1410
01:33:58.493 --> 01:33:59.536
Get them trucks out the road!
让他们把卡车驶离道路！
（阿拉楚阿县界）


1411
01:33:59.744 --> 01:34:01.579
- Turn around! - What are you boys doing?
-回去！ -你们这帮小子想干嘛？
（阿拉楚阿县界）


1412
01:34:01.746 --> 01:34:02.706
You need to get on out the road!
你们得闪开这条路！


1413
01:34:02.914 --> 01:34:04.165
We got business to take care of over there!
我们去那边有正经事要办！


1414
01:34:04.332 --> 01:34:05.333
Turn around!
回去！


1415
01:34:05.500 --> 01:34:07.460
You ain't bringing all this into our town.
你们不能把这些带到我们镇上来。


1416
01:34:07.627 --> 01:34:08.962
Oh, yeah, we are.
哦，好吧，我们就带了。


1417
01:34:09.129 --> 01:34:12.507
We're looking for a colored fugitive name of Jesse Hunter.
俺们在找一个叫杰西·亨特的有色人种逃犯。


1418
01:34:12.674 --> 01:34:14.300
Our coloreds are law-abiding folk!
我们这里的有色人种都是守法的！


1419
01:34:14.467 --> 01:34:16.177
Bronson don't want you.
我布朗森不需要你们。


1420
01:34:16.344 --> 01:34:17.387
Now turn around!
现在，掉头回去！


1421
01:34:19.597 --> 01:34:21.224
What are you all going down on us for?
为什么你们这么对待俺们？


1422
01:34:21.391 --> 01:34:23.727
Y'all gonna protect niggers?
你们都想庇护黑鬼吗？


1423
01:34:23.893 --> 01:34:26.312
That ain't no way to treat a white man!
你们不能这样对待白人！


1424
01:34:26.479 --> 01:34:27.981
Oh, hell,he ain't here.
该死，他不在这儿。


1425
01:34:28.148 --> 01:34:30.817
I'm gonna remember this!
俺会记住的！


1426
01:34:37.323 --> 01:34:39.409
Now, go on in there with them.
现在，和他们一起合影吧。


1427
01:34:41.494 --> 01:34:42.829
Ready?
预备？


1428
01:35:20.450 --> 01:35:21.409
Hey, Bobby!
嘿，波比！


1429
01:35:21.576 --> 01:35:23.286
Hey, we're goin' back over.You comin'?
嘿，俺们要去翻个遍。你来吗？


1430
01:35:23.495 --> 01:35:24.829
Yeah.I'll be along in a bit.
好的，我马上就来。


1431
01:35:24.996 --> 01:35:26.331
You save me some.
你们给我留点儿。


1432
01:35:26.498 --> 01:35:29.334
Them niggers, they runnin' like chicken, boy!
那些黑鬼，他们像小鸡一样逃了，小子！


1433
01:35:29.501 --> 01:35:32.103
They in the swamp now. We're gonna get 'em!
他们现躲在沼泽里。俺们会抓到他们的


1434
01:36:03.835 --> 01:36:05.929
Them's church bells.
教堂在敲钟。


1435
01:36:05.995 --> 01:36:07.997
My daddy's ringin' 'em.
我爸爸敲的。


1436
01:36:08.206 --> 01:36:09.290
Them crackers be ringin' them bells.
是那些坏蛋们敲的。


1437
01:36:09.399 --> 01:36:11.184
Now, you stay put, you hear?
现在，你们都呆好了，听见了吗？


1438
01:36:11.251 --> 01:36:13.962
No. That's my daddy in his church.
不。那是我爸爸在他的教堂里。


1439
01:36:14.129 --> 01:36:15.688
He tellin' us it's safe to come home.
他告诉我们现在可以回家了。


1440
01:36:15.755 --> 01:36:17.090
No, Denny, Lee Ruth...
不，丹尼，李.露丝...


1441
01:36:17.257 --> 01:36:18.675
Maybelle!
梅布尔！


1442
01:36:18.842 --> 01:36:20.109
Denny, come back here.
丹尼，回到这儿来。


1443
01:36:20.176 --> 01:36:21.428
Denny, no.Come back here.
丹尼，不。回到这儿来。


1444
01:36:24.764 --> 01:36:26.474
Bust it up, boys!
砸了它，小子们！


1445
01:36:29.102 --> 01:36:30.937
Bust it all up, now!
砸了它！马上！


1446
01:36:31.104 --> 01:36:32.897
Bust it all up!
把所有的都砸了！


1447
01:36:46.578 --> 01:36:48.580
Niggers!
黑鬼！


1448
01:37:03.261 --> 01:37:04.512
Come on. Git.
快走，孩子。


1449
01:37:26.493 --> 01:37:28.995
That's a fire, now,ain't it?
这把火怎么样？


1450
01:37:32.540 --> 01:37:35.377
Well, look,this come out perfect here.
你看，这样就好了。


1451
01:37:35.543 --> 01:37:36.836
13.
弄成13的形状


1452
01:37:37.003 --> 01:37:38.438
Then you pull that through there, see?
然后你把这头穿过这里，看见了吗？


1453
01:37:38.505 --> 01:37:41.007
Now, you pull on one of those.
现在，你拉一下。


1454
01:37:41.174 --> 01:37:42.258
That's perfect.That's good.
完成了，很好。


1455
01:37:42.425 --> 01:37:43.802
There you go.Pull tight.
就这样。拉紧。


1456
01:37:43.968 --> 01:37:45.804
There you go. That's good.
就这样，很好。


1457
01:37:45.970 --> 01:37:47.806
Now you've got it, boy.
现在你已经学会了，小子。


1458
01:37:47.972 --> 01:37:49.307
There's your noose.
这就是你的套索。


1459
01:37:49.474 --> 01:37:50.850
Now you make one.
现在你自己做一个。


1460
01:37:51.017 --> 01:37:52.560
Just like this one.
就像这个。


1461
01:38:02.987 --> 01:38:04.823
Oh, that's a good one.
哦，这个很好。


1462
01:38:04.989 --> 01:38:06.950
That's a good one.
这个很好。


1463
01:38:07.992 --> 01:38:09.160
Good boy.
好孩子。


1464
01:38:10.620 --> 01:38:13.998
Here. Use these and cover yourself up.
拿着，用这个把自己盖住。


1465
01:38:14.165 --> 01:38:17.127
It's all right.You're all right.
会没事的，你们全会没事的。


1466
01:38:17.335 --> 01:38:19.671
Scrappie, I'm freezing.
斯卡比，我都快冻死了。


1467
01:38:19.838 --> 01:38:21.464
Scrappie, I'm hungry.
斯卡比，我饿了。


1468
01:38:23.299 --> 01:38:24.134
Quiet, y'all!
你们都别出声！


1469
01:38:24.300 --> 01:38:25.969
They're gonna hear us.
他们会听见我们的。


1470
01:38:52.495 --> 01:38:54.956
They done killed everybody.
他们都被害了。


1471
01:38:55.123 --> 01:38:57.042
Aunt Sarah,Big Baby, Sylvester.
萨拉阿姨，大宝贝，西尔维斯特。


1472
01:38:57.208 --> 01:38:58.835
Scrappie.
斯卡比。


1473
01:39:04.549 --> 01:39:05.759
Look.
看。


1474
01:39:16.019 --> 01:39:20.190
It's more than 50 children hidin' around in the swamp,
有超过50个孩子躲在沼泽里


1475
01:39:20.357 --> 01:39:22.025
and they been out here all night...
他们在外面待了一整夜…


1476
01:39:22.192 --> 01:39:23.568
with nothing to eat,
没吃没穿，


1477
01:39:23.735 --> 01:39:26.071
and they're cryin',and they're freezin'.
他们一直在哭，他们都在受冻。


1478
01:39:26.237 --> 01:39:28.531
What we gonna do?What we gonna do?
我们怎么办？我们怎么办？


1479
01:39:28.740 --> 01:39:30.367
Y'all be quiet now.
你们现在必须安静。


1480
01:39:30.575 --> 01:39:31.534
Now, hush!
现在，安静下来！


1481
01:39:31.701 --> 01:39:33.495
Hush. Just hush.
安静。只有安静。


1482
01:39:39.000 --> 01:39:40.418
Stop fighting.
别去战斗。


1483
01:39:47.008 --> 01:39:48.676
Arnett...
阿内特...


1484
01:39:48.843 --> 01:39:50.345
Front and center.
你位置很重要。


1485
01:39:55.475 --> 01:39:57.811
Quit crying, Arnett.
别哭了，阿内特。


1486
01:39:57.977 --> 01:40:01.690
You ain't a little boy no more. You a man.
你已不再是小孩了。你是个男人。


1487
01:40:01.898 --> 01:40:04.776
Now, you see any tears in these eyes?
现在，你眼中不应再有泪水。


1488
01:40:07.028 --> 01:40:09.823
I need you to be strong.
我需要你坚强。


1489
01:40:09.989 --> 01:40:12.992
You're my lieutenant,understand?
你现在是我的副官，明白吗？


1490
01:40:13.159 --> 01:40:14.202
Yes, sir.
是的，长官。


1491
01:40:18.957 --> 01:40:21.042
Now, you gather up these women and children.
现在，把这些妇女和孩子集合起来。


1492
01:40:21.209 --> 01:40:23.294
You're gonna move deep into the swamp.
你们将进入沼泽深处。


1493
01:40:30.135 --> 01:40:30.969
All right.
好吧。


1494
01:40:31.136 --> 01:40:33.304
We gots to move.
我们要行动了。


1495
01:40:33.471 --> 01:40:34.639
Get up.
起来。


1496
01:40:36.224 --> 01:40:38.309
Come on. Get up.
快点。起来。


1497
01:40:38.476 --> 01:40:39.561
Come on. Move.
快点。出发。


1498
01:40:39.728 --> 01:40:40.812
Let's go. Move!
我们走，出发！


1499
01:40:40.979 --> 01:40:42.163
I knew you'd be back.
我就知道你是我们的依靠。


1500
01:40:42.230 --> 01:40:43.815
It's gonna be all right.
会没事的。


1501
01:40:43.982 --> 01:40:46.276
Let's move it.Get him up.
我们都走，帮他站起来。


1502
01:40:46.484 --> 01:40:47.819
Oh, he's bad.
哦，他有残疾。


1503
01:40:47.986 --> 01:40:50.071
He ain't gonna last out here.
他在这里撑不了多久的。


1504
01:40:50.238 --> 01:40:52.073
Emma, there ain't nothin'the matter with me.
艾玛，我没有什么问题。


1505
01:40:52.240 --> 01:40:53.742
- I can walk.- Daddy.
-我能走。-爸爸。


1506
01:40:53.950 --> 01:40:55.118
There ain't no place to go.
没有别的地方可去。


1507
01:40:55.326 --> 01:40:57.037
You come too late!
你来得太迟了!


1508
01:40:57.203 --> 01:40:59.330
All right, Timothy.Upstairs with the Turners.
好了，蒂莫西。和特纳一家上楼去。


1509
01:40:59.497 --> 01:41:01.207
Put him upstairs, too,in the front.
把他也带上楼，你带路。


1510
01:41:01.374 --> 01:41:02.709
That's enough.That's enough.
够了。够了。


1511
01:41:02.876 --> 01:41:04.210
Let's go. Upstairs.
我们上楼去。


1512
01:41:04.377 --> 01:41:05.837
Everyone upstairs!
每个人都上楼！


1513
01:41:06.004 --> 01:41:08.339
And clean this place up. Look at this.
把这里收拾干净。看看这摊。


1514
01:41:08.506 --> 01:41:09.674
Clean this up.
收拾干净。


1515
01:41:09.841 --> 01:41:13.303
Oh, my God!This is not happening.
哦,我的上帝!这是不该发生的。


1516
01:41:13.470 --> 01:41:15.388
What's the matter with you?
你怎么回事？


1517
01:41:19.017 --> 01:41:20.810
I know you don't...
我知道你不...


1518
01:41:21.019 --> 01:41:24.314
I know you don't like having colored folks in the house,
我知道你不喜欢黑人进这幢房子，


1519
01:41:24.481 --> 01:41:25.815
but this is a serious time.
但现在是危急时刻。


1520
01:41:25.982 --> 01:41:27.359
Is that what you think,
你真是这么想的吗？


1521
01:41:27.525 --> 01:41:30.320
that I don't like livin' here 'cause of the colored folks?
我就因为这些黑人，而不喜欢住在这里吗？


1522
01:41:30.528 --> 01:41:31.654
Is that what you think?
这就是你想法吗？


1523
01:41:31.821 --> 01:41:32.822
Well, what is it, Mary?
那你说是什么？玛丽？


1524
01:41:33.031 --> 01:41:36.618
I am caring for the colored folks in my home!
我刚还在照顾在我家的黑人！


1525
01:41:36.785 --> 01:41:38.119
It's my home, too.
这也是我的家。


1526
01:41:38.286 --> 01:41:40.330
I know.Yes, it's your home.
我知道，这是你的家。


1527
01:41:40.497 --> 01:41:45.335
You all treat me like a guest in my own house.
你在我自己的家里，总把我当成客人。


1528
01:41:45.502 --> 01:41:48.630
I got news for you,John Wright.
我告诉你，约翰·赖特。


1529
01:41:48.838 --> 01:41:50.507
Carol is dead.
卡罗尔已经去世了。


1530
01:41:50.673 --> 01:41:54.677
She's dead.She ain't comin' back,
她死了。她不会再回来了，


1531
01:41:54.844 --> 01:41:56.805
and I ain't leavin'.
而我也不会走的。


1532
01:42:03.478 --> 01:42:05.397
Oh, God!
噢，上帝！


1533
01:42:11.403 --> 01:42:12.737
Put me down.
放我下来。


1534
01:42:12.904 --> 01:42:15.949
Put me down!
放我下来！


1535
01:42:16.116 --> 01:42:16.950
Emma!
艾玛！


1536
01:42:17.117 --> 01:42:18.910
Emma!
艾玛！


1537
01:42:20.078 --> 01:42:22.205
Put me down.
放我下来。


1538
01:42:22.372 --> 01:42:24.374
I hear you're hiding folk,Mr. Wright.
我听说你家在藏着什么人。赖特。


1539
01:42:24.541 --> 01:42:25.875
I need you to put away old James here.
我要你把老詹姆斯也藏起来。


1540
01:42:26.042 --> 01:42:27.168
You're misinformed.
你误会了。


1541
01:42:27.335 --> 01:42:28.545
You best take him.Go hide in the woods.
你最好带他走。躲到树林里去。


1542
01:42:28.712 --> 01:42:30.213
No. I don't want to go in there.
不。我不想去那儿。


1543
01:42:30.380 --> 01:42:31.214
Take him, and go hide in the swamp.
带他躲到沼泽里去。


1544
01:42:31.381 --> 01:42:32.549
I ain't gonna go in that house!
我不想进那幢房子！


1545
01:42:32.716 --> 01:42:35.218
- John Wright?- What?
-约翰.赖特？-什么？


1546
01:42:35.427 --> 01:42:37.721
I know what you been doin' with my daughter.
我知道你对我女儿做了什么。


1547
01:42:37.929 --> 01:42:38.805
What?
什么？


1548
01:42:38.972 --> 01:42:40.974
- Hush now. - I can run like you.
-现在需要冷静。-我能像你一样跑。


1549
01:42:41.141 --> 01:42:42.809
No, you can't.
不，你不行。


1550
01:42:42.976 --> 01:42:45.854
Now, you gonna get us killed.Just hush!
你这样会让我们都被杀的。你要冷静！


1551
01:42:46.021 --> 01:42:47.355
Come on, Mr. Wright.
算了吧，赖特先生。


1552
01:42:47.522 --> 01:42:48.857
You the massa around here.
你是这里的乡绅。


1553
01:42:49.024 --> 01:42:50.525
I ain't a massa of nothin'.
我算个狗屁乡绅。


1554
01:42:50.692 --> 01:42:51.776
You best git while you can.
你们最好趁早离开。


1555
01:42:51.943 --> 01:42:53.528
- What's the matter, Mr. Wright? - Git!
-怎么了？赖特先生？-快走！


1556
01:42:53.695 --> 01:42:54.612
Don't he owe you enough to save his life?
难道他不值得你救吗？


1557
01:42:54.779 --> 01:42:55.822
You son of a bitch.
你个王八蛋，


1558
01:42:55.989 --> 01:42:57.532
How much it take for you to hide this man?
要付你多少钱？你才愿意藏下这个人？


1559
01:42:57.741 --> 01:42:59.534
$10? 15?

1560
01:42:59.701 --> 01:43:01.703
How about 60, goddamn 50?

1561
01:43:01.870 --> 01:43:03.079
I'm gonna blow your head off!
我要打爆你的脑袋！


1562
01:43:03.288 --> 01:43:05.540
This man's life worth one acre of land?
这人的一条命还不值你的一英亩地？


1563
01:43:05.707 --> 01:43:09.335
Hide the man, John,for God's sake.
收留他吧，约翰，看在上帝的份上。


1564
01:43:09.502 --> 01:43:11.421
Let him in.
让他进来。


1565
01:43:18.011 --> 01:43:19.220
Come on.
来吧。


1566
01:43:22.891 --> 01:43:23.725
Come on.
快走。


1567
01:43:23.892 --> 01:43:24.726
No, Mama.
不，妈妈。


1568
01:43:24.893 --> 01:43:25.727
Come on, baby.
快走，宝贝。


1569
01:43:25.894 --> 01:43:27.103
No, Mama. It's all right.You go on.
不,妈妈。没关系。你继续。


1570
01:43:27.270 --> 01:43:28.813
Go, Mama! I'm all right.
你去，妈妈！我没事的。


1571
01:43:28.980 --> 01:43:33.610
I can't go in there, Mama! Take care of Papa.
我不能进那幢房子，妈妈！照顾好爸爸。


1572
01:43:33.777 --> 01:43:34.569
Come on!
快来！


1573
01:43:34.736 --> 01:43:37.322
Come on, now. Git!
快点儿，块！


1574
01:43:37.489 --> 01:43:38.406
Go.
去吧。


1575
01:43:40.992 --> 01:43:42.952
I'll be all right, Mama.
我会没事的，妈妈。


1576
01:44:11.981 --> 01:44:14.526
What's the problem, boys? What's the matter?
有什么问题吗？小伙子们？怎么回事啊？


1577
01:44:14.693 --> 01:44:16.277
We want James Carrier.
我们要詹姆斯.凯利。


1578
01:44:16.444 --> 01:44:17.320
Right now.
快点。


1579
01:44:17.487 --> 01:44:19.489
Well, I ain't seen him.Hell, I ain't seen nobody.
我没见过他，我这儿压根儿就没人。


1580
01:44:19.656 --> 01:44:20.548
Damn it, John.
该死的，约翰。


1581
01:44:20.615 --> 01:44:23.159
We caught his daughter.
俺们抓住了他的女儿。


1582
01:44:23.368 --> 01:44:24.661
We know he's here!
俺们知道他在这里！


1583
01:44:24.869 --> 01:44:27.163
What did y'all peckerwoods do to her?
你们这些乡巴佬对她做了什么


1584
01:44:27.330 --> 01:44:28.498
Where's she at, damn it?
该死的，她在哪儿？


1585
01:44:28.665 --> 01:44:30.041
Where's she at, Ellis?
她在哪儿，艾利斯？


1586
01:44:31.710 --> 01:44:34.546
Come on now!It's her daddy we after!
得了吧! 我们要找的是她爸爸！


1587
01:44:34.713 --> 01:44:37.090
Explain to me why you want to lynch a cripple.
告诉我你为什么要对一个瘸子动私刑。


1588
01:44:37.257 --> 01:44:39.901
We ain't lynchin' nobody don't need to be lynched, John.
俺们不会对任何人用私刑，也不需要用私刑，约翰。


1589
01:44:40.009 --> 01:44:41.052
I just don't see no sense in it.
我只是觉得这没什么意义。


1590
01:44:41.219 --> 01:44:43.680
John, James Carrier was in that house...
约翰，詹姆斯·凯利在那房子里…


1591
01:44:43.888 --> 01:44:45.140
with Sylvester and Jesse Hunter!
还有西尔韦斯特和杰西.亨特！


1592
01:44:45.306 --> 01:44:49.144
Yeah. We just want to ask him a few questions, John.
是的。我们只是想问他几个问题，约翰。


1593
01:44:49.310 --> 01:44:50.437
That's all.
仅此而已。


1594
01:44:50.603 --> 01:44:54.858
Well, that's all fine,but I ain't got him.
那很好，但他不在我这里。


1595
01:44:55.025 --> 01:44:56.359
All right, boys!
行了，孩子们！


1596
01:44:56.526 --> 01:44:57.360
Stay back!
退后！


1597
01:44:57.527 --> 01:44:59.863
You get off my porch!Get off my...
你们滚出我家门廊! 滚出我的…


1598
01:45:00.030 --> 01:45:01.364
Don't you come near!
你胆敢再上前一步！


1599
01:45:01.531 --> 01:45:02.699
Simmer down!
别发火！


1600
01:45:02.907 --> 01:45:04.325
Johnny,you want these boys...
约翰尼，你想让这些小伙子们...


1601
01:45:04.492 --> 01:45:05.827
to go through your wife and children?
搜查你的妻子和孩子们吗？


1602
01:45:05.994 --> 01:45:07.328
Is that what you want?
难道你想要这样？


1603
01:45:07.495 --> 01:45:08.371
Come on! Bring him out!
算了吧！你就把他叫出来吧！


1604
01:45:08.538 --> 01:45:10.331
We will! That's what we're gonna do!
我们会的！这就是我们要做的！


1605
01:45:10.498 --> 01:45:12.333
You give me your word,
你向我保证，


1606
01:45:12.500 --> 01:45:15.920
all you want to do is question him? Yes?
你们就是想盘问他吗？是吗？


1607
01:45:19.758 --> 01:45:22.343
That's more like it!
这才像话！


1608
01:45:22.510 --> 01:45:23.845
Y'all wait here.
你们都等在这里。


1609
01:45:24.012 --> 01:45:25.847
Get that nigger out here!
把那个黑鬼带到这儿来！


1610
01:45:26.014 --> 01:45:29.809
He was in the house the whole time.
他一直在房子里。


1611
01:45:29.976 --> 01:45:31.144
Get that damn nigger!
带那该死的黑鬼出来！


1612
01:45:40.320 --> 01:45:41.321
John!
约翰！


1613
01:45:41.488 --> 01:45:42.822
John, where are you going?
约翰，你要去哪里？


1614
01:45:42.989 --> 01:45:44.657
You're not going to let those people have him?
你不能让那些人带走他吧？


1615
01:45:44.824 --> 01:45:46.159
Mary, please.
玛丽，请别这样。


1616
01:45:46.326 --> 01:45:49.120
If I don't, they'll come in here and shoot us all.
如果我不这么做，他们会进来把我们都杀了。


1617
01:45:49.287 --> 01:45:50.830
They just want to ask him some questions.
他们只是想问他一些问题。


1618
01:45:50.997 --> 01:45:54.292
I'll be with him to make sure they don't do more than that.
我会和他在一起，确保他们不会做更过分的事。


1619
01:45:54.459 --> 01:45:55.710
I'll be with him.
我陪他一起。


1620
01:45:59.130 --> 01:46:00.256
Now, James...
现在，詹姆斯...


1621
01:46:01.966 --> 01:46:05.804
We got old Sarah over here, resting her soul.
我们把老萨拉阿姨带到这里，愿她灵魂安息。


1622
01:46:05.970 --> 01:46:09.307
If you don't tell us where this Jesse boy is,
如果你不告诉我们杰西在哪，


1623
01:46:09.474 --> 01:46:12.227
we're gonna have to put you in there with her.
我们得把你和她一起埋进去。


1624
01:46:12.394 --> 01:46:14.104
It's a big box!
这是口大棺材！


1625
01:46:16.481 --> 01:46:18.775
Why ain't my sister buried?
为什么我的姐姐还不下葬？


1626
01:46:18.942 --> 01:46:21.236
'Cause you ain't buried her yet.
因为你没有给她下葬。


1627
01:46:21.403 --> 01:46:22.737
Dig a hole,nigger.
挖个坑，黑鬼。


1628
01:46:22.904 --> 01:46:25.532
I ain't got but one good arm.
我只有一只胳膊能用。


1629
01:46:25.699 --> 01:46:27.742
We ain't got but one good shovel.
俺们也只有一把好铲子。


1630
01:46:29.452 --> 01:46:31.371
Come on. Get up here,you old crow,
来吧。就在这儿挖，你这个老乌鸦


1631
01:46:31.538 --> 01:46:33.056
and dig your own hole.
把你自己的坑也挖了。


1632
01:46:33.123 --> 01:46:34.057
Come on!
快点儿！


1633
01:46:34.124 --> 01:46:35.917
Show us what you're made of.
让俺们看看你的本事。


1634
01:46:36.084 --> 01:46:37.502
Come on! Let's go!
来吧！我们干吧！


1635
01:46:37.669 --> 01:46:40.839
Grab that shovel.Let me see what you can do.
拿起那把铲子，让俺看看你有多能干。


1636
01:46:41.005 --> 01:46:42.340
Get him goin'!
让他干完活！


1637
01:46:42.507 --> 01:46:44.926
Whoa! He's eager, ain't he?
呜哇！他很卖力，对吧？


1638
01:46:58.898 --> 01:47:00.984
James, stop it.
詹姆斯，住手。


1639
01:47:01.151 --> 01:47:05.530
Just trying to help him put that shovel in the ground.
俺只是想帮他拿起地上的铁锹。


1640
01:47:05.697 --> 01:47:06.990
James, listen here.
詹姆斯，听我说。


1641
01:47:07.198 --> 01:47:11.494
I want you to tell these boys where Jesse Hunter is.
你要告诉是我，杰西.亨特在哪里。


1642
01:47:11.661 --> 01:47:13.830
He was in that house with you, wasn't he?
他是不是和你在房子里？


1643
01:47:13.997 --> 01:47:16.666
Now, tell me, hear me? Listen up.
现在，告诉我？听清楚了？


1644
01:47:16.833 --> 01:47:19.836
James, you tell them something, hmm?
詹姆斯，你跟他们说点什么


1645
01:47:20.045 --> 01:47:21.880
James, look at me!
詹姆斯，看着我！


1646
01:47:22.047 --> 01:47:24.841
You tell them something,for God's sake.
看在上帝的份儿上，你就说吧。


1647
01:47:25.050 --> 01:47:26.342
I'm pleading to you.
我恳求你。


1648
01:47:26.509 --> 01:47:30.347
Sheriff,I can't lie to you.
治安官，我不能对你撒谎。


1649
01:47:30.513 --> 01:47:32.891
I ain't never met the man.
我从未看见那个人。


1650
01:47:36.811 --> 01:47:37.979
Fair enough.
说得好。


1651
01:47:38.146 --> 01:47:40.315
Stop! Duke!
住手！杜克！


1652
01:47:40.482 --> 01:47:43.318
God! What's the matter with you, Duke?
上帝！你怎么回事？杜克？


1653
01:47:43.485 --> 01:47:45.320
What the hell is the matter with you?
你到底是怎么回事？


1654
01:47:45.487 --> 01:47:46.488
Oh, hush up, John.
哦，安静，约翰。


1655
01:47:46.654 --> 01:47:48.823
You done went and turned nigger lover on us.
你的黑鬼情人让你背叛了俺们。


1656
01:47:48.990 --> 01:47:50.325
Ever since your wife passed away,
自从你的前妻过世后，


1657
01:47:50.492 --> 01:47:51.826
you ain't been the same.
你就和以前不一样了。


1658
01:47:51.993 --> 01:47:53.328
I'm goin' home, y'all.
俺要回家了，各位。


1659
01:47:53.495 --> 01:47:55.205
Nigger lover, my ass!
让黑鬼情人舔俺的屁股吧！


1660
01:47:56.498 --> 01:47:58.875
You stupid piece of white trash!
你这个愚蠢的白人垃圾！


1661
01:47:59.042 --> 01:48:00.960
What did you call me?
你管俺叫什么？


1662
01:48:01.127 --> 01:48:03.463
Don't you nigger lover me,you white trash!
难道你没有黑鬼情人，你个白色垃圾！


1663
01:48:03.630 --> 01:48:04.547
Come on!
来吧！


1664
01:48:14.974 --> 01:48:17.811
Think of who you are.Think of who you are.
想想你是谁。想想你是谁。


1665
01:48:17.977 --> 01:48:19.354
Think of what you're saying.
想想你刚才说的。


1666
01:48:19.521 --> 01:48:22.357
Don't do this.
别再这样了。


1667
01:48:22.524 --> 01:48:23.358
Nigger lover.
黑鬼的情人。


1668
01:48:23.525 --> 01:48:25.235
Nigger lover!
黑鬼的情人！


1669
01:48:25.402 --> 01:48:28.029
Whose side you on,Johnny Wright?
你站在哪一边？约翰尼.赖特？


1670
01:48:28.238 --> 01:48:30.323
Don't even care a white man got shot!
我才不在乎再一个白人中枪！


1671
01:48:30.490 --> 01:48:31.950
You forgetting who you are, Johnny?
你忘了自己是谁了，约翰尼？


1672
01:48:36.996 --> 01:48:38.331
Go home, Johnny.
回家去,约翰尼。


1673
01:48:38.498 --> 01:48:40.959
You go home right now.
你马上回家。


1674
01:48:44.504 --> 01:48:46.589
You got the money that man owes me?
你来还那人欠我的钱吗？


1675
01:48:48.049 --> 01:48:50.677
Y'all gonna pay me for all the money I'm losing?
你们要把我损失的钱还给我吗？


1676
01:48:50.844 --> 01:48:51.678
Hell, no!
见鬼去，不！


1677
01:48:51.845 --> 01:48:53.346
Killin' all of my customers,
你们把我的主顾都给杀了，


1678
01:48:53.513 --> 01:48:54.431
runnin' 'em off.
都被赶走了。


1679
01:48:54.597 --> 01:48:56.474
You watch who you call white trash, boy!
我管谁叫白色垃圾，小子！


1680
01:48:56.641 --> 01:48:58.476
That's right.
没错。


1681
01:48:58.643 --> 01:49:01.146
Just 'cause you rich off nigger money,
就因为你靠黑鬼的钱发财，


1682
01:49:01.312 --> 01:49:04.315
you think you better than all the rest of us?
你就以为你比我们都强吗?


1683
01:49:04.482 --> 01:49:05.775
That's right!
没错！


1684
01:49:05.942 --> 01:49:08.820
You get all the money in Florida, Johnny Wright,
你即使把全佛罗里达的钱都赚走了，约翰尼，


1685
01:49:08.987 --> 01:49:10.655
you still ain't nothin'...
你还是什么都不是...


1686
01:49:10.822 --> 01:49:13.408
but a dirt-floor cracker!
就是一个肮脏的地板下的臭虫！


1687
01:49:13.575 --> 01:49:16.411
Shopkeeper!
小店主！


1688
01:49:19.611 --> 01:49:22.611
星期一

1689
01:50:01.331 --> 01:50:03.124
Hey, now, wake up.
嘿，快醒醒。


1690
01:50:03.291 --> 01:50:04.542
Come on.
起来。


1691
01:50:04.709 --> 01:50:07.837
Come on. We got to go.Time to wake up.
起来。我们得走了。该醒醒了。


1692
01:50:08.046 --> 01:50:09.964
We're going to go this way.
我们走这条路。


1693
01:50:12.008 --> 01:50:15.345
Gertie, where are we going?
葛蒂，我们要去哪里？


1694
01:50:15.512 --> 01:50:16.680
Keep quiet.
保持安静。


1695
01:50:17.972 --> 01:50:19.683
We're going to go this way.
我们走这条路。


1696
01:50:49.003 --> 01:50:51.715
I ain't got no bullets.
我没有子弹了。


1697
01:51:17.615 --> 01:51:18.450
Share!
要分享！


1698
01:51:18.616 --> 01:51:19.951
Hey, y'all be quiet!
嘿，你们都别出声！


1699
01:51:20.118 --> 01:51:21.453
Y'all be quiet.
你们要安静。


1700
01:51:21.619 --> 01:51:23.621
Want them crackers to hear you?
你们想让那坏蛋们听见你们吗？


1701
01:51:23.788 --> 01:51:27.684
Bring the train to the old road near Kelly's pond.
我去把火车引领到凯利家池塘附近的旧铁路上。


1702
01:51:27.751 --> 01:51:32.088
Get there, listen for the engine whistle.
你们想办法到那里，注意火车开动声。


1703
01:51:32.255 --> 01:51:34.716
That's on the other side of Sumner, Mr. Wright.
那可是在萨姆纳镇的另一头，赖特先生。


1704
01:51:34.883 --> 01:51:36.718
How we gonna do that?
我们怎么到那里？


1705
01:51:36.885 --> 01:51:38.720
You're askin' us to take these children...
你要我们带着这些孩子...


1706
01:51:38.887 --> 01:51:40.513
through all them crackers?
在那些坏蛋们眼皮底下通过？


1707
01:51:40.680 --> 01:51:43.533
Can't stop near Rosewood.It's Kelly's pond or nowhere.
不能再靠近紫檀镇了。只能在凯利池塘停车了。


1708
01:51:43.600 --> 01:51:46.436
No men on the train. That's the plan.
没人会注意那辆火车。这是计划好的。


1709
01:51:46.603 --> 01:51:49.939
How we know we can trust you, Mr. Wright?
我们怎么知道可以信任你，赖特先生?


1710
01:51:50.148 --> 01:51:52.025
Got no choice.
别无选择。


1711
01:51:52.192 --> 01:51:53.943
In the trenches now.
现在就是在战壕里。


1712
01:51:54.110 --> 01:51:58.406
8:00. That's three hours.
晚上8点。还有3个小时。


1713
01:51:59.991 --> 01:52:01.826
Get these folks there.
把这些乡亲们送到那里。


1714
01:52:01.993 --> 01:52:04.621
I'll bring the train.
我去把火车引领来。


1715
01:52:07.999 --> 01:52:10.835
If you're lying,I'm comin' for ya.
如果你撒谎，我饶不过你。


1716
01:52:11.002 --> 01:52:13.338
Soldier, if I'm lying,you're dead.
士兵，如果我骗了你，你现在已经死了。


1717
01:52:13.505 --> 01:52:14.547
Yes, sir.
是的，长官。


1718
01:52:16.007 --> 01:52:17.842
We agreed about the men?
我们是同一战线的。


1719
01:52:18.009 --> 01:52:20.011
Yes, sir.
是的，长官。


1720
01:52:20.178 --> 01:52:21.554
That includes you.
那也包括你。


1721
01:52:26.017 --> 01:52:28.645
Johnny, we just went through there this morning.
约翰尼，我们今天上午已经去过那里了，


1722
01:52:28.812 --> 01:52:30.397
It ain't nothin' but ashes and smoke.
它到处是灰烬和浓烟。


1723
01:52:30.563 --> 01:52:31.731
Town's in purgatory.
整个镇子就像是炼狱。


1724
01:52:31.898 --> 01:52:34.359
Billy, it's a real simple thing,we do it right.
比利，很显然，我们在行正义之事。


1725
01:52:34.526 --> 01:52:36.027
They got boys on all the bridges,
他们派人在所有的桥上，


1726
01:52:36.194 --> 01:52:37.487
all the main roads lookin' for colored men.
所有的主干道上寻找黑人。


1727
01:52:37.696 --> 01:52:39.322
We go in at night,round back to Sumner,
我们晚上进去，绕回萨姆纳，


1728
01:52:39.531 --> 01:52:40.573
pick up the women and children,
接上妇女和孩子，


1729
01:52:40.740 --> 01:52:41.908
sweep them off to Gainesville.
把他们带到盖恩斯维尔去。


1730
01:52:42.075 --> 01:52:43.201
He's talkin' about Sumner!
他在说萨姆纳!


1731
01:52:43.368 --> 01:52:46.204
That's where the whole damn thing started!
整件事就是从那里开始的!


1732
01:52:46.371 --> 01:52:49.165
You're askin' us to risk our engine, Johnny!
你让我们拿机车冒险，约翰尼！


1733
01:52:49.332 --> 01:52:50.667
Who are you Bryce brothers,
你以为是谁?布莱斯兄弟，


1734
01:52:50.834 --> 01:52:52.293
a couple of rich boys playin' on your train?
难道几个富家小孩子上你的火车玩吗？


1735
01:52:52.460 --> 01:52:53.461
To hell with you.
你见鬼去吧。


1736
01:52:53.628 --> 01:52:54.629
You boys puffin' around the countryside...
你的孩子们可以走在乡间小路上...


1737
01:52:54.796 --> 01:52:55.839
wavin' and tootin' your whistle?
向你挥手，向你吹口哨。


1738
01:52:56.005 --> 01:52:57.006
To hell with you!
见鬼去吧你！


1739
01:52:57.215 --> 01:52:58.842
These are real folks dyin',
这些乡亲们正在死去，


1740
01:52:59.050 --> 01:53:00.719
women and children ain't done nothin' wrong to no soul.
他们的女人和孩子能有什么错。


1741
01:53:00.885 --> 01:53:01.845
That ain't fair, Johnny!
这不公平，约翰尼！


1742
01:53:02.012 --> 01:53:03.847
Don't talk to me about fair, Billy!
别跟我谈什么公平，比利！


1743
01:53:04.014 --> 01:53:08.727
They shot Sarah Carrier down like a dog on her own porch!
他们在莎拉·凯利家的门廊上像杀狗一样把她打死了!


1744
01:53:08.893 --> 01:53:12.355
I ain't asking you to risk your train!
我不是让你拿火车冒险!


1745
01:53:12.522 --> 01:53:15.150
I'm asking you to risk your asses!
我是在让你们冒生命危险!


1746
01:53:36.004 --> 01:53:38.506
Think they gonna let the women and children through?
你觉得他们会让女人和孩子通过吗?


1747
01:53:40.508 --> 01:53:42.302
I don't know.
我不知道。


1748
01:53:47.599 --> 01:53:49.893
Wait, wait.
等等。


1749
01:53:57.359 --> 01:53:58.777
Stay here.
呆在这里。


1750
01:54:10.789 --> 01:54:11.873
Damn.
该死。


1751
01:54:12.082 --> 01:54:13.750
Let's go. We gotta move.
快点。我们必须得走了。


1752
01:54:31.309 --> 01:54:32.644
How far out are we?
我们还要走多远？


1753
01:54:32.811 --> 01:54:34.604
About 40 minutes.
大约要40分钟。


1754
01:54:34.771 --> 01:54:37.315
Can't we move this thing any faster?
我们就不能再快一点儿吗？


1755
01:54:37.482 --> 01:54:38.858
Push that throttle, J.B.
推动那个油门，J.B.


1756
01:54:39.025 --> 01:54:40.985
Don't you be telling us how to run our train, Johnny.
别告诉我们该怎么开火车，约翰尼。


1757
01:54:41.152 --> 01:54:43.446
We gotta take it easy on her.She ain't been acting right.
我们得悠着点。这辆车状况不太好。


1758
01:54:43.613 --> 01:54:44.781
Oh, she ain't?
哦，不会出故障吧？


1759
01:54:44.989 --> 01:54:47.826
You boys been treating this train like a little sister...
你们对待它就像对你们的姐妹...


1760
01:54:47.992 --> 01:54:49.452
since I known you.Get her moving.
自从我认识你们以来。让这车跑快点。


1761
01:54:49.561 --> 01:54:50.887
She can't handle it!
它会受不了的！


1762
01:54:50.995 --> 01:54:53.289
Get this son of a bitch moving.
加快速度，


1763
01:54:53.456 --> 01:54:56.000
J.B., give her a little.
J.B.给它加点儿速度。


1764
01:55:04.009 --> 01:55:05.068
Feel better?
行了吧？


1765
01:55:05.135 --> 01:55:06.594
Yeah.
是的。


1766
01:55:07.762 --> 01:55:09.681
I feel better.
我感觉好多了。


1767
01:55:14.019 --> 01:55:15.020
I'm tired.
我累了。


1768
01:55:15.186 --> 01:55:17.188
I don't feel like going.
我不想再走了。


1769
01:55:17.355 --> 01:55:18.648
Hush up.
安静。


1770
01:55:18.815 --> 01:55:20.191
Hush up, be quiet.
安静，别出声。


1771
01:55:34.497 --> 01:55:36.499
That truck coming, boys.
卡车来了，小伙子们。


1772
01:55:38.001 --> 01:55:39.335
Watch out, now.
现在都注意了。


1773
01:55:39.502 --> 01:55:40.962
Watch yourself.
小心点。


1774
01:55:47.427 --> 01:55:48.845
Get on up.
上去。


1775
01:56:16.289 --> 01:56:17.348
Come on.
过来。


1776
01:56:19.417 --> 01:56:21.669
Wait, wait.
等等。


1777
01:56:35.100 --> 01:56:37.185
Might as well come look.
最好来看一眼。


1778
01:56:39.229 --> 01:56:41.606
Make room for my boy here.
让一下，让这孩子看一下，


1779
01:57:18.810 --> 01:57:20.854
Why you cryin', boy?
你哭什么？小子。


1780
01:57:21.021 --> 01:57:22.605
There's babies in there.
里面还有婴儿。


1781
01:57:24.399 --> 01:57:28.153
A nigger is a nigger, boy.None of us like it.
黑鬼就是黑鬼，儿子，我们没人喜欢他们。


1782
01:57:28.319 --> 01:57:31.114
God made the world the way it is,
上帝创造了这个世界，


1783
01:57:31.281 --> 01:57:32.966
and we just got to live in it.
而只有我们能生活在其中。


1784
01:57:33.033 --> 01:57:38.788
You get as old as I am,you become a man...
当你像我这么大的时候，要当一个男人...


1785
01:57:38.955 --> 01:57:41.791
you're gonna learn a lot of things.
你会学到很多东西。


1786
01:57:46.046 --> 01:57:48.590
A nigger is a nigger, boy.
黑人就是黑人，小子。


1787
01:57:48.757 --> 01:57:50.842
That's the way.
就是那样。


1788
01:57:52.218 --> 01:57:54.929
You understand me,Emmett?
你懂我的话吗？艾美特？


1789
01:57:55.096 --> 01:57:56.222
You understand me?
你理解我吗？


1790
01:58:02.062 --> 01:58:03.396
She's overheating!
它都发烫了！


1791
01:58:06.191 --> 01:58:07.108
Damn it!
该死的！


1792
01:58:07.275 --> 01:58:08.318
Damn it, I told you!
该死的，我跟你说过！


1793
01:58:08.526 --> 01:58:10.528
We're stopping,we're stopping!
我们开不动了，我们停住了！


1794
01:58:10.695 --> 01:58:12.238
We can't stop.No, no.
我们不能停。不，不。


1795
01:58:12.405 --> 01:58:13.948
Don't you get it?
你难道不知道吗？


1796
01:58:14.115 --> 01:58:15.784
Don't you get it?
你难道不懂吗？


1797
01:58:15.950 --> 01:58:17.243
We are stopped!
我们停住了！


1798
01:58:17.410 --> 01:58:19.454
We can't go anywhere!
我们哪儿都去不了！


1799
01:58:19.621 --> 01:58:21.748
It's your fault!
这都怪你！


1800
01:58:21.915 --> 01:58:23.333
Your fault!
怪你！


1801
01:58:24.709 --> 01:58:27.128
Goddamn counterbalance pin!
该死的平衡栓！


1802
01:58:28.380 --> 01:58:29.506
Damn it!
该死的！


1803
01:58:29.673 --> 01:58:33.009
J.B., leave him alone.You gotta check the engine.
J.B.,离他远点。你得检查引擎。


1804
01:58:42.227 --> 01:58:45.730
Don't you heathens touch my porch.
你们这些异教徒不许碰我的门廊。


1805
01:58:45.897 --> 01:58:46.731
Step aside.
闪开。


1806
01:58:46.898 --> 01:58:48.441
We hear you're hiding niggers in here.
俺们听说你这里藏着黑鬼，


1807
01:58:48.608 --> 01:58:51.778
Turn around, Earl, before I send us both to damnation.
转过身去，厄尔，在我把我们都送进地狱之前。


1808
01:58:54.364 --> 01:58:55.990
Jesus Christ, Mary.
上帝，玛丽。


1809
01:58:56.157 --> 01:58:58.326
That damn thing ain't loaded anyway.
反正那玩意也没上子弹。


1810
01:58:58.493 --> 01:59:00.203
Oh, yes, it is.
哦，是的，就是。


1811
01:59:00.370 --> 01:59:02.122
You got any niggers in there, Mary?
里面有黑鬼吗，玛丽？


1812
01:59:02.288 --> 01:59:05.225
Willing to kill a white woman to find out, Bobby?
你想杀了一个白人妇女而进去查看吗？波比？


1813
01:59:05.291 --> 01:59:06.710
Now turn around and get home.
现在你们掉头，回家。


1814
01:59:06.918 --> 01:59:08.378
Get on, get!
想试试，来！


1815
01:59:09.796 --> 01:59:12.757
Come on, Earl.Ain't no niggers around here.
算了吧，厄尔。附近也没看见什么黑鬼。


1816
01:59:12.924 --> 01:59:14.217
Come on, y'all.
大家都撤。


1817
01:59:14.384 --> 01:59:15.385
Come on, now.
现在，走吧。


1818
01:59:15.552 --> 01:59:19.973
You men best hope the Lord feels merciful come Judgment Day.
你们最好祈祷在审判日到来时上帝会发发善心。


1819
01:59:21.516 --> 01:59:23.143
Hush.
安静。


1820
01:59:36.448 --> 01:59:38.658
Everybody front and center.
所有人都列队。


1821
01:59:41.369 --> 01:59:42.620
Lieutenant.
副官。


1822
01:59:47.042 --> 01:59:48.209
Where's Arnett?
阿内特呢？


1823
01:59:48.418 --> 01:59:49.836
He gone.
他不见了。


1824
01:59:51.296 --> 01:59:52.422
Where's Minnie?
明妮在哪里？


1825
01:59:55.717 --> 01:59:57.260
Stay put.
呆着别动。


1826
02:00:10.106 --> 02:00:13.401
What y'all boys need to get this engine running again?
你们需要什么才能让引擎重新运转起来？


1827
02:00:13.568 --> 02:00:14.903
Somethin' we ain't got.
有些东西我们没有。


1828
02:00:15.070 --> 02:00:17.489
Counterbalance pin.
平衡栓，


1829
02:00:17.655 --> 02:00:20.325
What is a counterbalance pin?
什么是平衡销？


1830
02:00:20.492 --> 02:00:21.968
Oh, it ain't nothin'.
哦，也不算什么。


1831
02:00:22.035 --> 02:00:25.579
Piece of metal about this long.
就是一根大概这么长的铁棍。


1832
02:00:39.511 --> 02:00:41.888
Be quiet. Minnie, be quiet.
安静。明妮，安静。


1833
02:01:02.325 --> 02:01:06.079
All right, y'all men, listen up.Let's call it a night.
好了，伙计们，听好了。今晚就到此为止吧。


1834
02:01:06.246 --> 02:01:08.248
Bobby, Earl, give me a hand.Get these men out of here.
鲍比，厄尔，帮俺个忙。让这些人出去一下。


1835
02:01:08.415 --> 02:01:09.499
Y'all go home.
你们回家吧。


1836
02:01:09.708 --> 02:01:12.502
Get these men out of here.Go on.
把这些人带出去。继续。


1837
02:01:12.669 --> 02:01:15.296
No more camping out in my town! You hear me?
不许在我们镇上露营!你听到我说的吗?


1838
02:01:15.463 --> 02:01:17.173
Hush, y'all, hush!
安静，你们都安静！


1839
02:01:17.340 --> 02:01:18.675
All right,I see you in there.
好了，俺好像看到他了。


1840
02:01:18.842 --> 02:01:20.427
What you up to, Duke? What do you see?
你打算干什么？杜克？你看见了什么？


1841
02:01:20.593 --> 02:01:22.303
Hold still, now. Right up against that tree, y'all.
现在不要动。就靠在那棵树上。


1842
02:01:22.470 --> 02:01:23.596
Go get him.
去抓住他。


1843
02:01:28.560 --> 02:01:30.395
Minnie.Minnie's back.
明妮。明妮回来了。


1844
02:01:32.939 --> 02:01:34.357
Where you been?
你去哪儿了？


1845
02:01:34.524 --> 02:01:35.608
What...
怎么了...


1846
02:01:37.193 --> 02:01:40.113
He gonna get killed looking for you.
他会因为找你而送命的。


1847
02:01:49.372 --> 02:01:52.375
Show you to rape my wife.
让你强奸我老婆。


1848
02:01:56.546 --> 02:01:58.048
Put him up!
把他吊起来！


1849
02:02:02.552 --> 02:02:04.929
Simmer down, y'all!
你们都消消气！


1850
02:02:05.096 --> 02:02:06.598
I had a nice quiet town here,
本来我这个镇子好好的，


1851
02:02:06.765 --> 02:02:09.809
but you put an end to that,didn't you, boy?
你一来就全完了，对吧？小子？


1852
02:02:09.976 --> 02:02:11.311
Wasn't no colored boy...
黑人男孩…


1853
02:02:11.478 --> 02:02:13.204
had nothin do to with what happened there.
…跟那里发生的事没有任何关系。


1854
02:02:13.271 --> 02:02:14.147
Shut up.
闭嘴。


1855
02:02:14.314 --> 02:02:15.565
Shut up, Jesse.
闭嘴，杰西。


1856
02:02:15.732 --> 02:02:17.275
That ain't my name.
那不是我的名字。


1857
02:02:27.035 --> 02:02:28.953
Clear a path.
让开一条道。


1858
02:02:29.120 --> 02:02:30.413
Get back, get back.
退后，退后。


1859
02:02:30.580 --> 02:02:32.332
Run the nigger up.
把那黑鬼吊起来。


1860
02:02:37.629 --> 02:02:39.547
Ha, damn you!
哈，你个该死的！


1861
02:02:39.714 --> 02:02:41.049
Come on,you stupid horse!
快点，你个愚蠢的马！


1862
02:02:41.216 --> 02:02:44.135
Just shoot the damn horse.
杀了那匹该死的马。


1863
02:02:44.302 --> 02:02:46.429
Booker T., go!
布克.T.快跑！


1864
02:02:55.563 --> 02:02:58.566
Goddamn.
该死的。


1865
02:03:21.589 --> 02:03:23.925
That is one strong buck.
这家伙很结实。


1866
02:03:24.092 --> 02:03:25.719
Why won't he die?
为什么他还不死？


1867
02:03:25.885 --> 02:03:28.054
He gonna die, he gonna die.His neck ain't that thick.
他就要死了。他会死的。他的脖子没那么结实。


1868
02:03:28.221 --> 02:03:30.015
Oh, he'll die,
哦，他会死的，


1869
02:03:30.181 --> 02:03:33.785
only he probably didn't have nothing to do with it.
只是有可能，他什么都没做，


1870
02:03:33.852 --> 02:03:38.064
Well, truth be told,none of 'em did.
也许，真相会揭示出他们中谁也没做。


1871
02:03:38.231 --> 02:03:40.650
What the hell does that mean, Ellis?
你他妈这是什么意思？艾利斯？


1872
02:03:40.859 --> 02:03:42.819
It means, James,
就是说，詹姆斯，


1873
02:03:43.028 --> 02:03:44.779
that you know as well as I do...
你我心里都清楚...


1874
02:03:44.988 --> 02:03:47.157
what Fanny'd been doing lunch times.
范妮总是在吃午饭时间做什么勾当。


1875
02:03:47.323 --> 02:03:50.160
Some of y'all know better than others!
你们中有些人甚至更清楚！


1876
02:03:50.326 --> 02:03:51.536
That's right.
没错。


1877
02:03:51.703 --> 02:03:53.038
Should have never listened to her.
就不该听她的胡说八道。


1878
02:03:53.204 --> 02:03:54.748
That woman's a wildcat.
那个女人是个靠不住的女人。


1879
02:04:52.514 --> 02:04:54.224
Booker T.!
布克.T!


1880
02:05:00.647 --> 02:05:02.148
Shoot him!
开枪！


1881
02:05:05.610 --> 02:05:08.363
Sorry I had to say it that way, James,
原谅我这么说，詹姆斯，


1882
02:05:08.530 --> 02:05:12.200
but this thing's gone far enough.
但这件事情已经闹得够严重了。


1883
02:05:15.954 --> 02:05:18.415
Fanny lied...
范妮在说谎...


1884
02:05:18.581 --> 02:05:21.918
to you, to me,the whole damn town.
对你，对我，对整个镇子。


1885
02:05:25.463 --> 02:05:30.051
Deep down, I don't think I believed her from the start.
说实在的，我从一开始就有点儿不相信她。


1886
02:05:30.218 --> 02:05:31.720
If that's how you feel,
如果她如你所说，


1887
02:05:31.828 --> 02:05:34.114
why'd you take her word for this, Ellis?
为什么你还把她说的当成证言？艾利斯？


1888
02:05:34.180 --> 02:05:36.474
What choice I got, huh?
我能有什么选择？呃？


1889
02:05:36.641 --> 02:05:38.768
I am the sheriff.
我是治安官。


1890
02:05:38.935 --> 02:05:40.186
Damn.
该死。


1891
02:05:40.353 --> 02:05:42.313
My badge.
我的警徽呢。


1892
02:05:48.319 --> 02:05:51.114
What's gonna keep it in place?
怎么能让它保持正常运行？


1893
02:05:52.407 --> 02:05:54.034
Prayer.
祈祷。


1894
02:06:04.419 --> 02:06:05.920
Move it!
快跑！


1895
02:06:19.893 --> 02:06:21.895
Come on, move!
快点，跑啊！


1896
02:06:33.948 --> 02:06:36.868
Get on board, get on board,get on board.
快上车，上车，上车！


1897
02:06:38.119 --> 02:06:41.373
Get 'em on,get 'em on!
大家都上车，大家都上车！


1898
02:06:41.539 --> 02:06:44.042
Come on, move.
快点儿。


1899
02:06:45.877 --> 02:06:46.936
Get on, get on!
上去，上去！


1900
02:06:47.003 --> 02:06:49.339
Come on. We ain't gonna sit on the track all night.
快点，我们可不会整晚在铁道上等你们。


1901
02:06:49.506 --> 02:06:50.507
Move!
快！


1902
02:06:53.843 --> 02:06:54.761
Get them on!
把他们拉上去！


1903
02:06:54.928 --> 02:06:56.304
Quickly!
快点儿！


1904
02:06:58.807 --> 02:07:00.100
Let's go!
我们走！


1905
02:07:00.266 --> 02:07:01.768
Let's go. Let's get the hell out of here.
快走，快离开这鬼地方。


1906
02:07:59.451 --> 02:08:02.078
You can't come on! You can't come on!
你不能上来！你不能上来！


1907
02:08:02.245 --> 02:08:03.371
Let me on this train!
我要搭上这列火车！


1908
02:08:03.538 --> 02:08:04.748
I said get down!
我说了，下去！


1909
02:08:04.914 --> 02:08:08.852
If they find men on this train,they'll kill everyone!
如果他们发现这列火车有成年男人，他们会杀了所有的人！


1910
02:08:08.918 --> 02:08:09.961
Get off!
滚开！


1911
02:08:14.966 --> 02:08:17.218
Please!
救命啊！


1912
02:08:17.385 --> 02:08:19.346
Stop the train!
把火车停下吧！


1913
02:08:30.607 --> 02:08:33.234
Get back.If they find men on this train,
退后。如果他们发现火车上有男人，


1914
02:08:33.401 --> 02:08:35.670
they'll kill all the women and children!
他们会杀了所有的女人和孩子!


1915
02:08:35.778 --> 02:08:37.854
You can't come on here!
你们不能上这趟列车！


1916
02:08:45.622 --> 02:08:47.207
No!
不！


1917
02:08:48.458 --> 02:08:49.626
Get down,get down!
趴下，趴下！


1918
02:08:56.883 --> 02:08:58.301
What the hell you doing?
你他妈在干什么？


1919
02:08:58.510 --> 02:09:01.471
This is a war!We're in the trenches!
这是战争！我们在同一战壕里！


1920
02:09:27.038 --> 02:09:28.206
Jesus Christ!
上帝啊！


1921
02:09:28.373 --> 02:09:29.766
Come on, girl.
加大马力，铁丫头。


1922
02:09:32.585 --> 02:09:34.671
Child, stay down.Stay down.
孩子，趴着。趴着。


1923
